1
00:01:01,314 --> 00:01:06,314
Tafsiri na explosiveskull
www.OpenSubtitles.org

2
00:01:13,200 --> 00:01:16,932
<i>Ulimwengu mzima
ni mkusanyiko wa kumbukumbu</i>

3
00:01:16,966 --> 00:01:20,865
<i>kwamba alikuwepo,
na kwamba nimempoteza.</i>

4
00:01:20,899 --> 00:01:23,100
<i>Lolote roho zetu
zimeundwa nalo,</i>

5
00:01:23,134 --> 00:01:25,731
<i>yake na yangu ni sawa.</i>

6
00:01:26,067 --> 00:01:28,998
<i>Njia ya kujikweza kiasi
kufungua hadithi yetu...</i>

7
00:01:29,033 --> 00:01:31,632
<i>lakini siku zote
nimekuwa na kipaji cha mambo ya maigizo.</i>

8
00:01:31,665 --> 00:01:34,334
<i>Unaona, hii ni hadithi</i> yetu<i>...</i>

9
00:01:34,365 --> 00:01:36,266
<i>ya Tessa na yangu.</i>

10
00:01:36,301 --> 00:01:38,134
<i>Ni hadithi
uliyoisikia hapo awali,</i>

11
00:01:38,167 --> 00:01:41,033
<i>iliyorithiwa kutoka kwa Wagiriki,
kupitia Shakespeare,</i>

12
00:01:41,067 --> 00:01:43,766
<i>akina Bronte, Jane Austen.</i>

13
00:01:44,200 --> 00:01:47,799
<i>Ni hadithi ya msichana mdogo
akigundua uhuru wake,</i>

14
00:01:47,832 --> 00:01:50,766
<i>huru kutoka kwa vifungo
vya mzazi wake dhalimu...</i>

15
00:01:50,799 --> 00:01:54,365
<i>na kuahidiwa kwa mvulana
ambaye ni wazi hampendi.</i>

16
00:01:54,400 --> 00:01:56,832
<i>Anakutana na kijana
mzuri wa kuvutia sana</i>

17
00:01:56,865 --> 00:01:59,100
<i>anayemvutia kupindukia...</i>

18
00:01:59,134 --> 00:02:03,034
<i>ingawa anawakilisha
kila kitu anachokichukia.</i>

19
00:02:03,066 --> 00:02:05,100
<i>Anampenda sana,</i>

20
00:02:05,134 --> 00:02:07,301
<i>anajitoa kwake,</i>

21
00:02:07,332 --> 00:02:10,100
<i>na hatimaye
anasalitiwa naye</i>

22
00:02:10,134 --> 00:02:12,233
<i>na kuachwa akiwa amevunjika moyo.</i>

23
00:02:12,865 --> 00:02:17,067
<i>Ila ni yeye ambaye
anaangamizwa na hila yake.</i>

24
00:02:17,533 --> 00:02:20,000
<i>Wakati inapohisiwa kama
kila kitu kimepotea,</i>

25
00:02:20,033 --> 00:02:24,266
<i>wawili hao huungana tena
na kuishi kwa furaha milele.</i>

26
00:02:24,300 --> 00:02:28,365
<i>Kama nilivyosema,
hadithi uliyoisikia hapo awali.</i>

27
00:02:28,400 --> 00:02:30,731
<i>Tofauti pekee ni...</i>

28
00:02:30,966 --> 00:02:33,100
<i>hii si hadithi hiyo.</i>

29
00:03:21,765 --> 00:03:24,033
Hujambo. Naweza kukuuliza swali?

30
00:03:24,067 --> 00:03:26,332
- Ondoka hapa.
- Namtafuta mtu.

31
00:03:26,366 --> 00:03:28,133
Ondoka hapa!

32
00:03:45,967 --> 00:03:49,731
Wuu! Hakika haionekani
kama Krismasi huku nje,

33
00:03:49,765 --> 00:03:51,866
joto hili lote
tulilokuwa nalo.

34
00:03:51,899 --> 00:03:54,300
Unajua, nachukia joto.

35
00:03:54,332 --> 00:03:57,265
Joto huwafanya watu
wafanye mambo ya ajabu.

36
00:03:57,300 --> 00:03:59,699
Huu!

37
00:04:11,133 --> 00:04:13,233
Asante... Asante!

38
00:04:13,731 --> 00:04:15,832
Samahani.

39
00:04:18,865 --> 00:04:21,233
Samahani! Bwana, unaweza
uzuia lifti hiyo, tafadhali!

40
00:04:21,265 --> 00:04:23,365
Mpumbavu!

41
00:04:27,832 --> 00:04:30,033
Asante.

42
00:04:30,765 --> 00:04:33,199
Je, umeniita
mpumbavu?

43
00:04:33,233 --> 00:04:35,033
Samahani?

44
00:04:35,067 --> 00:04:37,966
Umeniita hivi sasa
mpumbavu.

45
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:40,067
Ee, hapana. Sikufanya hivyo.

46
00:04:40,665 --> 00:04:43,365
Ndiyo, nadhani
niliwaza tu.

47
00:04:43,399 --> 00:04:45,699
Nadhani hivyo.

48
00:04:46,033 --> 00:04:49,000
Unajua, <i>nilikuwa</i> najaribu
kuuzuia lifti kwa ajili yako.

49
00:04:49,033 --> 00:04:51,134
Hakika ulikuwa unafanya hivyo.

50
00:04:53,832 --> 00:04:56,000
Tazama, nisamehe.
Ni siku yangu ya kwanza.

51
00:04:56,033 --> 00:04:58,000
Najaribu tu
kuvutia.

52
00:04:58,033 --> 00:05:01,798
Naam, hakika
umefanikiwa katika hilo.

53
00:05:03,365 --> 00:05:05,665
Mpumbavu.

54
00:05:12,132 --> 00:05:13,300
Hapana, hapana, hapana, hapana...

55
00:05:13,333 --> 00:05:15,067
- Unafanya kazi hapa?
- Mshangao.

56
00:05:15,100 --> 00:05:16,266
Tessa!

57
00:05:16,300 --> 00:05:18,033
Karibu katika
Uchapishaji wa Vance.

58
00:05:18,067 --> 00:05:19,699
Habari. Kimberly, sivyo?

59
00:05:19,732 --> 00:05:21,300
Kumbukumbu nzuri sana.
Nimevutiwa.

60
00:05:21,333 --> 00:05:22,966
Ndiyo, yeye anavutia
sana.

61
00:05:23,000 --> 00:05:23,899
Ninyi wawili mnafahamiana?

62
00:05:23,934 --> 00:05:26,233
Ee... sisi ni marafiki wa zamani.

63
00:05:26,266 --> 00:05:28,699
Sasa, ikiwa ninyi mabibi
mtaniruhusu?

64
00:05:28,732 --> 00:05:30,300
- Je, una shauku ya kuanza?
- Ndiyo.

65
00:05:30,333 --> 00:05:32,766
Hebu tukutambulishe
kwa bosi.

66
00:05:32,798 --> 00:05:36,033
Nyamaza kabisa
na unisikilize!

67
00:05:36,067 --> 00:05:38,766
Huenda huu usiwe
wakati mzuri wa utambulisho.

68
00:05:38,800 --> 00:05:42,000
Kwa nini nisikuonyeshe
ofisi yako?

69
00:05:42,033 --> 00:05:43,934
Trevor!

70
00:05:43,966 --> 00:05:46,067
Naishughulikia.

71
00:05:50,333 --> 00:05:52,165
Naomba radhi kwa vurugu hizi.

72
00:05:52,199 --> 00:05:53,834
Tumekuwa na upungufu
wa wanagenzi hivi karibuni,

73
00:05:53,867 --> 00:05:55,300
na tuna kazi nyingi
zilizolimbikizwa.

74
00:05:55,333 --> 00:05:56,966
Hiyo inaonekana kama wazimu kwangu.

75
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:59,100
Watu ninaowajua wangefanya lolote
kupata uanagenzi hapa.

76
00:05:59,132 --> 00:06:00,665
Najua, ni kwamba tu Vance

77
00:06:00,699 --> 00:06:02,732
ana tatizo hili dogo la

78
00:06:02,766 --> 00:06:04,132
kuwafuta kazi baada ya siku moja.

79
00:06:04,165 --> 00:06:05,399
Lakini hiyo haitakutokea
wewe.

80
00:06:05,432 --> 00:06:07,365
Nina hisia nzuri
kuhusu hili.

81
00:06:07,399 --> 00:06:09,834
Lakini kama nilivyosema
wakati wa mahojiano,

82
00:06:09,867 --> 00:06:11,665
kazi yako ni kusoma
maandishi matano kwa wiki,

83
00:06:11,699 --> 00:06:14,000
na kama utayapenda,
yatume tu kwangu.

84
00:06:14,033 --> 00:06:16,199
- Sawa.
- Jikoni iko pale mwisho wa ukumbi.

85
00:06:16,233 --> 00:06:18,365
Usiogope kuagiza
chakula chochote cha mchana.

86
00:06:18,399 --> 00:06:20,867
- Maswali yoyote?
- Uh, hapana. Niko sawa.

87
00:06:20,899 --> 00:06:23,100
Utaiweza hii.

88
00:07:19,033 --> 00:07:21,233
Mmm.

89
00:07:22,100 --> 00:07:24,165
Bwana Vance!

90
00:07:24,966 --> 00:07:26,999
Um... Um, nisamehe sana.

91
00:07:27,033 --> 00:07:28,399
Lazima nimepitiwa na usingizi.

92
00:07:28,432 --> 00:07:30,867
- Ni saa ngapi?
- 9:25.

93
00:07:32,733 --> 00:07:34,834
9:25?

94
00:07:34,867 --> 00:07:36,966
- Je, nimefukuzwa kazi?
- Keti chini.

95
00:07:37,500 --> 00:07:39,867
Unamaanisha kuniambia kuwa
umesoma vitabu vitatu

96
00:07:39,899 --> 00:07:42,033
na kufanya uchambuzi
ya vyote jana usiku,

97
00:07:42,065 --> 00:07:46,733
na unadhani <i>Carnival of Light</i>
cha Niko Tanaka ni kitabu kizuri?

98
00:07:46,766 --> 00:07:48,632
Ndiyo, ni kizuri. Ni, uh,

99
00:07:48,665 --> 00:07:50,065
ana sauti ya kipekee kabisa,

100
00:07:50,100 --> 00:07:52,199
inafanana sana na
kazi za mapema za Margaret Atwood,

101
00:07:52,233 --> 00:07:53,800
<i>The Edible Woman,</i>

102
00:07:53,834 --> 00:07:57,033
- <i>Surfacing...</i>
- Ninashuka sasa hivi.

103
00:07:57,533 --> 00:07:59,999
Chukua vitu vyako.
Njoo na mimi.

104
00:08:00,033 --> 00:08:02,132
Haya sasa.

105
00:08:07,300 --> 00:08:08,999
Habari za asubuhi, Bwana Vance.

106
00:08:09,033 --> 00:08:11,100
- Habari za asubuhi, bwana.
- Bwana Vance, nilikuwa tu...

107
00:08:11,132 --> 00:08:13,233
Nilikuwa najiuliza ikiwa tuna muda
wa kurudi kwenye...

108
00:08:13,266 --> 00:08:14,800
Ingia.

109
00:08:14,834 --> 00:08:17,233
Kwa sababu inanibidi nichukue
chaja yangu ya simu kule...

110
00:08:17,266 --> 00:08:19,966
Oh, tunafunga mlango!

111
00:08:21,432 --> 00:08:23,834
Ushauri mdogo wa kazi.

112
00:08:23,867 --> 00:08:26,365
- Hmm?
- Inasaidia ikiwa huvae nguo zile zile kila siku.

113
00:08:26,399 --> 00:08:27,999
Hiyo, na kuoga.

114
00:08:31,432 --> 00:08:33,633
Um, tunaenda wapi?

115
00:08:33,666 --> 00:08:35,365
Kuna mkutano wa
uchapishaji wa kidijitali,

116
00:08:35,399 --> 00:08:37,700
na nahitaji kupata
fadhili kwa ajili ya upanuzi wangu.

117
00:08:41,799 --> 00:08:43,866
Potea hapa!

118
00:08:44,999 --> 00:08:48,066
Ni sehemu gani ya "Tumefunga"
ambayo hu...

119
00:08:48,100 --> 00:08:49,732
- Habari.
- Una kazi?

120
00:08:49,767 --> 00:08:51,700
Niko katikati ya
jambo fulani hivi.

121
00:08:51,732 --> 00:08:56,033
Hivyo basi, unajua, mbona usirudi
kesho?

122
00:08:56,066 --> 00:08:58,365
Au uingie tu sasa hivi.

123
00:09:03,232 --> 00:09:04,732
Niko sawa.

124
00:09:04,767 --> 00:09:07,600
Haya basi, itapunguza maumivu.

125
00:09:08,133 --> 00:09:10,399
Napenda maumivu.

126
00:09:10,432 --> 00:09:14,667
Haya, jiamulie mwenyewe,
wewe mwendawazimu wa kujitesa.

127
00:09:20,232 --> 00:09:22,133
Karibu tena Montgomery,
Bwana Vance.

128
00:09:22,166 --> 00:09:24,066
Nina vyumba vyako
tayari kwa ajili yako.

129
00:09:24,100 --> 00:09:26,767
Tulileta mashine ya kuchapishia
kwenye chumba cha Bwana Trevor Matthews.

130
00:09:26,799 --> 00:09:28,899
Kwa bahati mbaya, chumba cha
Bi. Young kilikuwa hakijatayarishwa,

131
00:09:28,932 --> 00:09:31,332
hivyo tumemhamishia kwenye chumba cha kifahari
kwa hisani ya uongozi.

132
00:09:31,365 --> 00:09:33,033
Je, Bwana Jiang
ameshajiandikisha?

133
00:09:33,066 --> 00:09:34,767
Naamini
yuko kwenye baa.

134
00:09:34,799 --> 00:09:35,999
Bila shaka yuko huko.

135
00:09:36,033 --> 00:09:38,200
Kwa hiyo mimi napata mashine ya kuchapishia
na wewe unapata chumba cha kifahari.

136
00:09:38,232 --> 00:09:39,667
Unafurahia hili,
sivyo?

137
00:09:39,700 --> 00:09:41,332
Hakika.

138
00:09:41,365 --> 00:09:43,166
Mpenzi, unajali
kumpeleka Tessa kufanya manunuzi?

139
00:09:43,200 --> 00:09:44,399
Anahitaji kitu
kwa ajili ya leo usiku.

140
00:09:44,432 --> 00:09:46,732
Nakuamini.

141
00:09:47,865 --> 00:09:49,999
Twende tukafurahi kidogo.

142
00:09:52,432 --> 00:09:54,133
Una uhakika
kwamba ninaweza kuingia?

143
00:09:54,166 --> 00:09:56,166
Kwa sababu sijawahi kufika
kwenye klabu ya usiku hapo awali.

144
00:09:56,200 --> 00:09:58,166
Lakini si wanakagua...?

145
00:09:58,200 --> 00:10:01,833
Utakuwa nasi.
Haitakuwa tatizo.

146
00:10:01,865 --> 00:10:04,365
Sikiliza, kabla ya kwenda nje,

147
00:10:04,732 --> 00:10:06,365
nilitaka tu
kukuambia jambo fulani.

148
00:10:06,399 --> 00:10:07,667
Sawa.

149
00:10:07,700 --> 00:10:09,799
Vance na mimi ni...

150
00:10:10,700 --> 00:10:12,799
zaidi ya wafanyakazi wenza.

151
00:10:13,133 --> 00:10:14,832
Oh.

152
00:10:14,865 --> 00:10:17,899
Ilikuwa ni mambo ya kazi tu
kwa miaka mingi,

153
00:10:17,932 --> 00:10:19,667
hasa baada ya
mke wake kufariki,

154
00:10:19,700 --> 00:10:22,633
kisha nilianza kusaidia
na mwanawe Smith,

155
00:10:22,667 --> 00:10:26,066
na, vyema, upendo unaweza
kukushangaza kweli.

156
00:10:26,100 --> 00:10:28,133
Ndiyo, unaweza.

157
00:10:31,832 --> 00:10:33,332
- Ndiye huyo?
- Mm-hmm.

158
00:10:33,365 --> 00:10:36,133
- Maskini.
- Ni mtoto mpendwa sana.

159
00:10:37,066 --> 00:10:39,166
Ohh.

160
00:10:39,200 --> 00:10:42,932
Nasubiri kwa hamu wakuone
kwenye rinda hili leo usiku.

161
00:10:42,966 --> 00:10:45,066
Ala!

162
00:10:45,500 --> 00:10:47,033
Tulisahau kukununulia chupi.

163
00:10:47,066 --> 00:10:48,999
Lakini nguo zangu zipo dobinini.

164
00:10:49,033 --> 00:10:51,299
Nikiondoka sasa, naweza kurudi haraka kwenye jengo la maduka...

165
00:10:51,332 --> 00:10:52,932
Ohoo, hapana, hapana, hapana. Hapana. Ni sawa tu.

166
00:10:52,966 --> 00:10:55,066
- Una uhakika?
- Ndiyo.

167
00:10:55,567 --> 00:10:59,066
Sawa, inaonekana basi tutakaa bila chupi.

168
00:11:05,033 --> 00:11:07,633
Siamini nimekuwa Vance kwa siku moja tu.

169
00:11:07,667 --> 00:11:11,100
Naam, Hardin alisema tutakuwa na bahati kuwa nawe.

170
00:11:11,133 --> 00:11:14,832
- Uliongea na Hardin.
- Hapana, Vance ndiye aliongea.

171
00:11:14,865 --> 00:11:16,667
Hakukuambia?

172
00:11:16,700 --> 00:11:19,200
Lazima alisahau.

173
00:11:50,899 --> 00:11:55,865
Ndiyo, mradi tu tufike kwenye mkutano ifikapo saa nane...

174
00:11:58,433 --> 00:12:00,265
Aisee.

175
00:12:00,299 --> 00:12:02,567
Umependeza sana.

176
00:12:03,399 --> 00:12:05,765
Lo, Trevor, hakika unajua jinsi ya kuwavutia wanawake.

177
00:12:05,798 --> 00:12:07,265
Tessa, unapendeza ajabu.

178
00:12:07,299 --> 00:12:09,166
Asante.

179
00:12:09,200 --> 00:12:11,299
Tunaondoka sasa.

180
00:12:22,299 --> 00:12:24,166
Hivyo basi, umeandika vitabu gani?

181
00:12:24,200 --> 00:12:26,299
Lo, hiki na kile.

182
00:12:33,100 --> 00:12:35,100
Nahisi kama nimekaa kwenye meza ya watoto.

183
00:12:35,133 --> 00:12:36,765
Asante.

184
00:12:36,798 --> 00:12:38,932
Hapana, sikumaanisha hivyo.
Pole.

185
00:12:38,966 --> 00:12:40,299
Nachukia klabu za usiku.

186
00:12:40,332 --> 00:12:42,400
Labda kwa sababu sijui kucheza dansi kabisa.

187
00:12:42,433 --> 00:12:44,798
Napenda mpira wa miguu wa Ohio, lakini nachukia klabu za usiku.

188
00:12:44,832 --> 00:12:46,932
Kwa nini tuko hapa?

189
00:12:47,865 --> 00:12:49,365
Yeye.

190
00:12:49,400 --> 00:12:51,366
Bwana Jiang.

191
00:12:51,400 --> 00:12:53,966
Familia yake inamiliki mfuko wa uwekezaji wenye thamani ya milioni 800

192
00:12:53,999 --> 00:12:57,400
na inafikiria kuwekeza katika upanuzi wa Vance.

193
00:12:57,433 --> 00:12:58,765
Unataka nikuletee kinywaji?

194
00:12:58,798 --> 00:13:00,232
Nitaendelea na maji tu.

195
00:13:00,265 --> 00:13:02,332
Ndivyo bajeti yangu inavyoruhusu siku hizi.

196
00:13:02,366 --> 00:13:04,366
Nilidhani wewe ni mwanafunzi unayelipwa.

197
00:13:04,400 --> 00:13:07,332
Utashangaa jinsi gharama za Uber zinavyoweza kuongezeka.

198
00:13:07,366 --> 00:13:09,765
Namaanisha, nitakuwa na bahati nikipata kiasi nilichotumia pekee.

199
00:13:12,832 --> 00:13:15,033
- Nitaenda.
- Ni nini hicho?

200
00:13:17,433 --> 00:13:19,731
Ngono Ufukweni.

201
00:13:20,433 --> 00:13:21,899
Pwani maridadi kwelikweli.

202
00:13:24,299 --> 00:13:27,999
Chukua mrija.
Kwenye alama yako, jiandae, nenda.

203
00:13:34,232 --> 00:13:36,631
Ni nzuri kwelikweli.

204
00:13:36,666 --> 00:13:38,899
Bwana Jiang, umepata fursa
ya kuangalia namba zangu bado?

205
00:13:38,932 --> 00:13:40,798
Kwa utabiri wa
kuongezeka kwa viwango vya riba...

206
00:13:41,865 --> 00:13:43,200
Tena. Tu...

207
00:13:43,232 --> 00:13:45,333
Ndiyo.

208
00:13:48,033 --> 00:13:50,832
Tutajivuruga
kwelikweli usiku wa leo!

209
00:14:08,265 --> 00:14:11,100
Haya, haya, tazama kile ambacho
paka amekileta.

210
00:14:11,133 --> 00:14:13,033
Huo ni msemo
wa kijinga mno.

211
00:14:13,066 --> 00:14:15,265
Kwa nini paka
aniburute popote?

212
00:14:15,301 --> 00:14:17,599
Karibu tena, kaka.

213
00:14:21,066 --> 00:14:23,166
Je, ulitukumbuka?

214
00:14:31,533 --> 00:14:33,865
Subiri.
Sielewi.

215
00:14:33,899 --> 00:14:35,999
Bila shaka huelewi.

216
00:14:36,899 --> 00:14:38,999
Hii ni nzuri sana!

217
00:14:42,033 --> 00:14:44,865
Ninahisi kucheza!

218
00:14:53,865 --> 00:14:55,400
Tabiri ni nani.

219
00:14:55,433 --> 00:14:56,966
Sawa, nitakupa dokezo.

220
00:14:56,999 --> 00:14:59,267
Anavutia kupindukia,
ana furaha sana,

221
00:14:59,301 --> 00:15:01,232
na <i>anapenda</i> sana kufanya mapenzi.

222
00:15:01,267 --> 00:15:03,731
- Mama Teresa.
- Hapana. Kha.

223
00:15:04,166 --> 00:15:06,301
Tazama!

224
00:15:06,333 --> 00:15:09,366
Najua, ninaonekana vizuri ajabu.
Sijala wanga kwa wiki nane hivi,

225
00:15:09,400 --> 00:15:11,366
- lakini ninajisikia vizuri mno.
- Lahaula.

226
00:15:11,400 --> 00:15:13,301
Ndiyo, ni kwa sababu ya kukosekana kwa
wanga na si kokeini yote hiyo.

227
00:15:13,333 --> 00:15:14,765
Je, huna mazulia
ya kutafuna?

228
00:15:14,798 --> 00:15:15,999
Je, huna
uume wa kunyonya?

229
00:16:19,234 --> 00:16:22,666
Nifanye nini
ili unisamehe?

230
00:16:22,698 --> 00:16:25,666
- Najua nimekuwa mbaya sana.
- Mbaya zaidi ya ubaya.

231
00:16:25,698 --> 00:16:28,333
Ndiyo, lakini unapenda
nikiwa mbaya.

232
00:16:28,366 --> 00:16:30,666
Unajua unanikumbuka.

233
00:16:34,731 --> 00:16:36,832
Sasa niondokee mbali.

234
00:16:38,133 --> 00:16:39,267
Ala!

235
00:16:39,301 --> 00:16:41,698
Nini hiki, Hardin?!

236
00:16:42,201 --> 00:16:44,301
Hardin, haukujali kufanya mapenzi nami
hapo awali, sivyo?

237
00:16:44,333 --> 00:16:46,631
Ah, ngoja nitabiri.

238
00:16:46,966 --> 00:16:49,167
Bado unasononeka
kwa ajili ya yule mwanamke mjeuri.

239
00:16:49,201 --> 00:16:50,832
Usizungumze kumhusu kabisa,
sawa?!

240
00:16:50,865 --> 00:16:53,666
Jiangalie. Unaonekana
kama mbwa mdogo aliyepotea.

241
00:16:53,698 --> 00:16:55,366
kuhusu binti fulani aliyejifanya bikira Maria na kugeuka kuwa malaya

242
00:16:55,400 --> 00:16:59,366
ambaye hata hakutaki!

243
00:16:59,400 --> 00:17:01,698
Ee, Mungu.

244
00:17:01,966 --> 00:17:04,333
Unatazama nini wewe, mwanachuo wa mwaka wa kwanza?

245
00:17:04,366 --> 00:17:09,233
Unataka nimuibe mpenzi wako? Basi geuka kule mara moja.

246
00:17:09,267 --> 00:17:11,366
Nimependeza sana.

247
00:17:22,066 --> 00:17:23,101
Tessa?

248
00:17:23,134 --> 00:17:24,865
Habari! Nilitaka tu, uh,

249
00:17:24,898 --> 00:17:26,267
Nilitaka tu kukujulisha

250
00:17:26,300 --> 00:17:28,366
kwamba nimependeza sana,

251
00:17:28,400 --> 00:17:29,932
na unapitwa na uhondo.

252
00:17:29,965 --> 00:17:32,032
Tessa, uko wapi?

253
00:17:32,066 --> 00:17:33,932
Wuuu! Mahali fulani ambapo haupo.

254
00:17:33,965 --> 00:17:36,766
Tess, ninajua mahali ulipo, naweza kukupata.

255
00:17:36,798 --> 00:17:39,300
Umekunywa kiasi gani?

256
00:17:39,333 --> 00:17:41,333
Sijui, labda tano hivi?

257
00:17:41,366 --> 00:17:42,366
Tano za nini?

258
00:17:42,400 --> 00:17:44,731
Uh, Ngono Ufukweni.

259
00:17:45,366 --> 00:17:48,134
Au ni Ngono nyingi Ufukweni?

260
00:17:48,766 --> 00:17:51,067
Hiyo ingekuwa ya kufurahisha!

261
00:17:51,101 --> 00:17:52,833
Umelewa chakari.

262
00:17:52,865 --> 00:17:55,134
Ooo, mambo, Hardin? Mimi ndiye amiri.

263
00:17:55,166 --> 00:17:57,400
Nimekuwa amiri usiku kucha.

264
00:17:57,432 --> 00:17:59,101
Amiri...

265
00:17:59,134 --> 00:18:00,731
Inaitwaje?

266
00:18:00,766 --> 00:18:03,665
Sijavaa nguo yoyote ya ndani!

267
00:18:03,699 --> 00:18:05,798
- Aaah! Ha ha ha! - Tess, uko na nani?

268
00:18:05,833 --> 00:18:07,798
Mbona hujanipigia simu?

269
00:18:07,833 --> 00:18:09,134
Nimekutumia ujumbe mara mia!

270
00:18:09,166 --> 00:18:10,334
Hujajibu!

271
00:18:10,365 --> 00:18:12,233
Kwa kweli inanibidi niondoke,

272
00:18:12,267 --> 00:18:14,865
lakini ilikuwa vyema kuzungumza nawe, Bwana Hardin Scott,

273
00:18:14,898 --> 00:18:16,233
basi kwaheri.

274
00:18:16,267 --> 00:18:19,598
Usifa... Te...

275
00:18:20,101 --> 00:18:21,334
Tessa.

276
00:18:21,365 --> 00:18:23,365
Trevor!

277
00:18:23,400 --> 00:18:26,101
Nimelewa, sijisikii vizuri, na nimeona pamba ya hedhi chini.

278
00:18:26,134 --> 00:18:27,798
- Naondoka. - Ndiyo, hapana, mimi pia.

279
00:18:27,833 --> 00:18:29,300
Je, tunaweza kuagiza huduma ya chakula chumbani?

280
00:18:29,333 --> 00:18:31,665
Mimi... ninataka viazi vya kukaanga

281
00:18:32,333 --> 00:18:34,665
na... aiskrimu.

282
00:18:34,699 --> 00:18:36,798
Aisee!

283
00:18:38,999 --> 00:18:41,798
Hakuna kitu kama aiskrimu ya vanila
saa tisa za alfajiri.

284
00:18:41,833 --> 00:18:44,067
Ndiyo,
ilisikika vizuri zaidi wakati huo.

285
00:18:46,233 --> 00:18:48,632
- Haya... Tessa.
- Hmm.

286
00:18:48,665 --> 00:18:50,365
- Tessa Young.
- Mm-hmm.

287
00:18:50,400 --> 00:18:52,665
Kwa nini basi
uko kwenye tasnia ya uchapishaji?

288
00:18:52,699 --> 00:18:54,833
Kweli, napenda kusoma...

289
00:18:56,067 --> 00:18:58,166
Hiyo inaeleweka.

290
00:18:58,500 --> 00:19:00,798
Kitabu chako unachokipenda zaidi ni kipi?

291
00:19:00,833 --> 00:19:04,932
Ni <i>Kanuni za
Uchumi</i> cha Alfred Marshall.

292
00:19:04,965 --> 00:19:06,898
- Hapana, siyo hicho.
- Ndiyo, ni hicho.

293
00:19:06,932 --> 00:19:09,034
Hapana, namaanisha...
Namaanisha, kama, hadithi za kubuni.

294
00:19:09,067 --> 00:19:11,034
Kama... Kama kitabu halisi.

295
00:19:11,067 --> 00:19:13,034
Sijihusishi na hadithi za kubuni.

296
00:19:13,067 --> 00:19:14,833
Namaanisha, umeona
vile ninavyovaa?

297
00:19:14,865 --> 00:19:16,365
- Wewe mpagani!
- Mpagani?

298
00:19:16,400 --> 00:19:18,134
Wewe mpagani!

299
00:19:18,166 --> 00:19:20,400
Hadithi za kubuni ni njia ya kutoroka
uhalisia,

300
00:19:20,432 --> 00:19:22,365
ni njia ambayo, kama,
unaweza kuishi maisha mia,

301
00:19:22,400 --> 00:19:23,932
au hata elfu moja.

302
00:19:23,965 --> 00:19:25,699
Sihitaji kuishi
maisha elfu moja.

303
00:19:25,731 --> 00:19:29,598
Sawa? Na heri
nitazame rangi ikikauka.

304
00:19:30,400 --> 00:19:33,266
Mimi, mmh, hiyo haikuwa...

305
00:19:33,299 --> 00:19:35,731
Hapana, mimi... hiyo haikupaswa
kutokea.

306
00:19:48,932 --> 00:19:50,865
Sikiliza, nakuambia,
najua ninachofanya.

307
00:19:50,898 --> 00:19:54,665
Tunapaswa tu kuiloweka
kabla haijaleta doa.

308
00:19:55,898 --> 00:19:57,266
Naweza kupata suruali yako?

309
00:19:57,299 --> 00:19:59,233
- Tessa...
- Nipe suruali yako!

310
00:19:59,266 --> 00:20:02,034
Vinginevyo itapata doa.

311
00:20:09,201 --> 00:20:11,632
<i>Tessa!</i>

312
00:20:11,665 --> 00:20:13,299
- <i>Tessa, fungua mlango.</i>
- Je, huyo ni Hardin Scott?

313
00:20:13,333 --> 00:20:16,034
<i>Fungua mlango!</i>

314
00:20:19,299 --> 00:20:21,134
Habari.

315
00:20:21,166 --> 00:20:24,833
Unajaribu kunifanya
nifukuzwe mahali hapa?

316
00:20:24,865 --> 00:20:27,699
Ndiyo,
ingia ndani, kwa nini usifanye hivyo?

317
00:20:27,731 --> 00:20:29,833
Hujambo...

318
00:20:31,400 --> 00:20:33,034
Habari, Hardin, sikukuona.
Umekuwaje?

319
00:20:33,067 --> 00:20:35,731
- Trevor huyu mpuuzi?!
- Wakati wa kuondoka, nadhani.

320
00:20:35,766 --> 00:20:37,134
- Naenda tu...
- Hapana, huendi.

321
00:20:37,166 --> 00:20:39,134
- Nataka tu kuzungumza naye!
- Hapana! Hapana...

322
00:20:39,166 --> 00:20:41,034
- Tessa... Tessa...
- Acha!

323
00:20:41,067 --> 00:20:43,632
- Hardin, nadhani huu ni mako...
- Potea zako.

324
00:20:43,665 --> 00:20:45,798
Wewe ni mpumbavu sana.
Kwa nini hata uko hapa?

325
00:20:45,833 --> 00:20:47,365
<i>Mimi</i> ni mpumbavu?

326
00:20:47,400 --> 00:20:49,731
Mimi siye ninayewatumia
wasichana waliolewa.

327
00:20:49,766 --> 00:20:51,699
Wewe... Unajua
kwamba si kila mwanamume

328
00:20:51,731 --> 00:20:54,034
anayejaribu kunivua chupi, sivyo?

329
00:20:54,067 --> 00:20:56,266
- Utashangaa.
- Huwezi kuniambia

330
00:20:56,299 --> 00:20:58,933
nani ninaweza na nisiyeweza kufanya naye ngono,
kwa sababu siyo shughuli yako tena!

331
00:20:58,967 --> 00:21:01,632
- Ulikuwa unaenda kufanya naye ngono?
- Oh, Mungu wangu!

332
00:21:01,665 --> 00:21:02,933
- Nini?
- Una wazimu!

333
00:21:02,967 --> 00:21:05,933
Unakwepa swali.

334
00:21:11,833 --> 00:21:13,232
Je, ikiwa nilikuwa?

335
00:21:13,266 --> 00:21:15,365
Nini?

336
00:21:16,833 --> 00:21:18,933
Umenisikia.

337
00:21:19,766 --> 00:21:22,000
Je, ikiwa nilikuwa?

338
00:21:22,034 --> 00:21:24,232
Nini,
hupendi hilo?

339
00:21:24,266 --> 00:21:27,200
Hupendi wazo la
mikono ya Trevor...

340
00:21:27,232 --> 00:21:29,299
kwenye mwili wangu wote?

341
00:21:30,034 --> 00:21:32,134
Ukinigusa?

342
00:21:36,731 --> 00:21:38,798
Nimeyakumbuka haya.

343
00:21:38,833 --> 00:21:42,134
- Tessa, umelewa.
- Mm-hmm. Kwa hiyo?

344
00:21:43,299 --> 00:21:45,665
Tess...

345
00:21:45,699 --> 00:21:47,000
Hmm!

346
00:21:47,034 --> 00:21:48,232
Hutaki hili?

347
00:21:48,266 --> 00:21:51,034
Bila shaka nataka hili,
lakini mimi...

348
00:21:51,333 --> 00:21:54,900
Hardin... una
chaguo mbili hapa.

349
00:21:56,365 --> 00:21:58,632
Aidha unifanye,

350
00:21:58,665 --> 00:22:00,866
au uondoke.

351
00:22:00,900 --> 00:22:02,967
Amua.

352
00:22:28,967 --> 00:22:31,067
Ohh.

353
00:22:36,299 --> 00:22:39,165
- Una kondomu?
- Una uhakika?

354
00:22:39,200 --> 00:22:41,200
- Kwa nini isiwe hivyo.
- Utanichukia kesho.

355
00:22:41,232 --> 00:22:44,200
Ndiyo, basi,
nakuchukia tayari.

356
00:22:58,799 --> 00:23:00,665
Niambie mimi ndiye pekee.

357
00:23:00,699 --> 00:23:02,731
Wewe ndiye pekee.

358
00:23:25,000 --> 00:23:27,099
Mmm.

359
00:23:42,834 --> 00:23:44,099
- Habari!
- <i>Habari za asubuhi!</i>

360
00:23:44,133 --> 00:23:45,866
- Kimberly!
- <i>Umeamka?</i>

361
00:23:45,900 --> 00:23:47,365
Ndiyo... hapana, ndiyo,
nimeamka muda mrefu uliopita.

362
00:23:47,400 --> 00:23:49,133
- <i>Tuonane chini baada ya dakika tano.</i>
- Dakika tano?

363
00:23:49,165 --> 00:23:51,066
- <i>Kuna tatizo?</i>
- Hapana, si tatizo.

364
00:23:51,099 --> 00:23:53,032
- <i>Tukutane kwenye ukumbi.</i>
- Sawa, nitashuka sasa hivi.

365
00:23:53,066 --> 00:23:55,767
- <i>Usichelewe.</i>
- Sawa. Kwaheri.

366
00:23:56,834 --> 00:23:58,933
Ala!

367
00:24:02,799 --> 00:24:04,933
Nguo zangu ziko wapi?!

368
00:24:10,133 --> 00:24:12,232
Oh!

369
00:24:14,165 --> 00:24:15,900
Tessa!

370
00:24:15,933 --> 00:24:18,032
Rudi kitandani.

371
00:24:19,200 --> 00:24:21,099
Tessa!

372
00:24:21,133 --> 00:24:23,632
Nini?!
Unataka nini?!

373
00:24:24,066 --> 00:24:27,032
Tessa yule mwingine.
Yule ambaye ni mkarimu?

374
00:24:27,066 --> 00:24:30,099
Ndiyo, basi,
amechelewa kazini.

375
00:24:34,299 --> 00:24:36,066
- Ziko wapi zangu...
- Kwa nini uko hivi...

376
00:24:36,099 --> 00:24:38,200
Hee! Faragha!

377
00:24:38,598 --> 00:24:41,133
Faragha.
Baada ya yale tuliyofanya jana usiku,

378
00:24:41,165 --> 00:24:42,299
unataka faragha?

379
00:24:42,333 --> 00:24:43,666
Usinikumbushe.

380
00:24:43,700 --> 00:24:45,400
Hee,
ulinipigia simu <i>mimi.</i>

381
00:24:45,432 --> 00:24:47,732
Sikukuambia
uje hapa.

382
00:24:47,767 --> 00:24:49,799
Sawa, naanza kupata hisia kwamba

383
00:24:49,834 --> 00:24:51,900
hujapendezwa kabisa na yaliyotokea jana usiku.

384
00:24:51,933 --> 00:24:53,232
Hapana, sijapendezwa nayo.

385
00:24:53,266 --> 00:24:54,866
Basi, unataka
tuzungumze kuhusu hilo?

386
00:24:54,900 --> 00:24:56,965
Hapana. Uliniumiza
na siwezi kukusamehe.

387
00:24:56,999 --> 00:24:58,666
- Ndivyo hivyo.
- Kwa hiyo jana usiku haikuwa na maana yoyote.

388
00:24:58,700 --> 00:24:59,999
Nilikuwa nimelewa.

389
00:25:00,032 --> 00:25:02,900
Nilikupigia simu,
ukaja hapa...

390
00:25:03,866 --> 00:25:04,999
Nilifanya kosa.

391
00:25:05,032 --> 00:25:06,700
Lakini ni dhahiri kuwa ulinikumbuka.

392
00:25:06,732 --> 00:25:08,732
Sikujua
nilichokuwa nikifanya.

393
00:25:08,767 --> 00:25:10,266
- Kuanzia kumbusu yule mwanamume, hadi...
- Nini?

394
00:25:10,299 --> 00:25:12,099
- Nini?
- Kuanzia kubusu?

395
00:25:12,133 --> 00:25:13,900
- Umesema nini?
- Sijasema lolote.

396
00:25:13,932 --> 00:25:15,633
- Umesema "kumbusu yule mwanamume."
- Hapana.

397
00:25:15,666 --> 00:25:17,299
- Nini?! T...
- Nahitaji kuondoka.

398
00:25:17,333 --> 00:25:19,299
Tessa, ngoja. Tessa!

399
00:25:19,333 --> 00:25:22,066
Tessa!

400
00:25:22,932 --> 00:25:25,032
Vaa nguo zako!

401
00:25:26,133 --> 00:25:28,299
- Ulimbusu nani?
- Hakuna mtu!

402
00:25:28,333 --> 00:25:29,700
- Alikuwa ni Trevor?
- Hapana!

403
00:25:29,732 --> 00:25:31,066
Tessa wangu asingeweza kabisa

404
00:25:31,099 --> 00:25:32,633
kumbusu mgeni asiyejulikana
kwenye klabu.

405
00:25:32,666 --> 00:25:34,799
Hakuna tena "Tessa wako"
tena!

406
00:25:34,834 --> 00:25:40,799
Ndiyo, basi, wakati ulikuwa ukimbusu huyo
mwanamume, mimi nilikuwa nafanya mapenzi na Molly.

407
00:25:43,365 --> 00:25:45,666
Potelea mbali!

408
00:25:50,232 --> 00:25:52,333
Shetani!

409
00:25:57,333 --> 00:25:59,633
- Oh!
- Pole.

410
00:26:01,133 --> 00:26:03,232
Habari.

411
00:26:03,599 --> 00:26:05,767
- Habari.
- Nimetuletea kahawa za latte.

412
00:26:05,799 --> 00:26:07,266
Asante.

413
00:26:09,700 --> 00:26:11,666
Oh. Asante.

414
00:26:11,700 --> 00:26:14,066
Hivyo basi, usiku wa kuvutia.

415
00:26:14,099 --> 00:26:17,999
Trevor, nina... masikitiko makubwa
kuhusu jana usiku.

416
00:26:18,032 --> 00:26:20,633
Hapana, usijali. Kama ningefika
kwenye chumba cha hoteli cha mpenzi wangu

417
00:26:20,666 --> 00:26:23,365
na nikamwona mwanamume aliye nusu uchi,
mwenye sura nzuri ajabu hapo,

418
00:26:23,400 --> 00:26:24,767
ningetenda kwa njia hiyo hiyo.

419
00:26:24,799 --> 00:26:26,732
Je, bado yupo
akinyemelea hapa?

420
00:26:26,767 --> 00:26:28,898
Je, nistahili kujificha
kwenye gari?

421
00:26:28,932 --> 00:26:30,633
Yeye ndiye anayepaswa
kujificha,

422
00:26:30,666 --> 00:26:32,898
na hatuko pamoja.

423
00:26:34,700 --> 00:26:37,133
Je, nyinyi wawili
mnafahamiana vipi?

424
00:26:37,165 --> 00:26:40,333
- Hardin alifanya kazi Vance mwaka jana.
- Kweli?

425
00:26:40,365 --> 00:26:42,865
Ndiyo. Nafasi sawa na yako,
kiukweli.

426
00:26:42,898 --> 00:26:44,365
Ni hadithi ya kusikitisha kiasi.

427
00:26:44,400 --> 00:26:47,299
Tulikuwa marafiki wa karibu sana,
na...

428
00:26:47,333 --> 00:26:49,133
kisha tukawa wapenzi,

429
00:26:49,165 --> 00:26:52,299
halafu nikapata
unywele mwekundu kwenye mto wangu.

430
00:26:52,333 --> 00:26:54,633
Inachekesha sana.

431
00:26:54,865 --> 00:26:56,365
Unajua, sikudhania ungekuwa
aina ya mvulana mtundu.

432
00:26:56,400 --> 00:26:59,732
Tutaacha hayo
kwa wakati mwingine.

433
00:27:00,365 --> 00:27:02,400
Shujaa wangu. Ohh.

434
00:27:02,432 --> 00:27:04,700
Kuna mwingine yeyote
anayejisikia kama kifo?

435
00:27:04,732 --> 00:27:07,633
Sijui nini nyinyi wawili mlimwambia
au kumfanyia Neil jana usiku,

436
00:27:07,666 --> 00:27:10,365
lakini ameandika hundi nono sana
kufadhili upanuzi wetu.

437
00:27:10,400 --> 00:27:12,700
Kazi nzuri.

438
00:27:25,032 --> 00:27:26,700
Unafanya nini hapa?

439
00:27:26,732 --> 00:27:28,732
Nahitaji ushauri fulani.

440
00:27:28,767 --> 00:27:30,200
Ushauri?

441
00:27:30,232 --> 00:27:32,066
Unataka ushauri
kutoka kwangu?

442
00:27:32,099 --> 00:27:33,865
Ndiyo.

443
00:27:33,898 --> 00:27:35,333
Nimekata tamaa kiasi hicho.

444
00:27:35,365 --> 00:27:37,633
Oh, matusi. Safi sana.

445
00:27:37,666 --> 00:27:39,798
Nilidhani wewe ni
mlaghai kwa muda.

446
00:27:39,833 --> 00:27:42,365
- Sikiliza, kaka, najua nime-
- Hapana, kaka wa kambo.

447
00:27:42,400 --> 00:27:45,333
Mimi si kaka yako.
Uliweka hilo wazi kabisa.

448
00:27:45,365 --> 00:27:47,833
Na kama ningekuwa Tessa,
singezungumza nawe tena, Hardin.

449
00:27:47,865 --> 00:27:50,766
- Hilo halisameheki.
- Unafikiri sijui hilo?!

450
00:27:50,798 --> 00:27:52,766
Najua nimeharibu kila kitu!
Najua!

451
00:27:52,798 --> 00:27:55,865
Hapokei simu zangu
wala jumbe.

452
00:27:55,898 --> 00:27:58,032
Nimegundua
alimbusu mwanamume fulani.

453
00:27:58,066 --> 00:28:00,666
Na... Na nilimwambia
nililala na Molly.

454
00:28:00,700 --> 00:28:02,965
- Ulilala na Molly?
- Hapana, <i>nilisema</i> nilifanya hivyo.

455
00:28:02,999 --> 00:28:04,666
Hiyo ndiyo hoja.
Sikufanya hivyo.

456
00:28:04,700 --> 00:28:06,165
Nilisema hivyo ili
kulipiza kisasi kwake,

457
00:28:06,200 --> 00:28:08,732
na n-nigundua
jinsi hiyo ilivyokuwa upumbavu.

458
00:28:08,766 --> 00:28:10,798
- Ndiyo.
- Oh, potelea mbali!

459
00:28:10,833 --> 00:28:14,333
Kwa hiyo utatoroka tu kama
unavyofanya kwa kila kitu. Sivyo?

460
00:28:14,365 --> 00:28:16,766
- Unakwenda wapi?
- London.

461
00:28:16,798 --> 00:28:18,965
Nilikuwa nitaenda
naye.

462
00:28:18,999 --> 00:28:20,798
Tutaonana mwakani.

463
00:28:20,833 --> 00:28:23,833
Hardin, unampenda kweli?

464
00:28:23,865 --> 00:28:25,965
Bila upuuzi.

465
00:28:26,999 --> 00:28:28,333
Ndiyo.

466
00:28:28,365 --> 00:28:30,099
Bila shaka
nampenda sana.

467
00:28:30,133 --> 00:28:33,365
Sijawahi kuhisi hivi
kuhusu mtu yeyote hapo awali!

468
00:28:33,400 --> 00:28:37,165
Natamani tu nisinge-
haribu kila kitu.

469
00:29:13,401 --> 00:29:15,699
Zingatia.

470
00:29:17,165 --> 00:29:18,666
Hodi hodi.

471
00:29:18,699 --> 00:29:20,333
- Habari.
- Habari.

472
00:29:20,365 --> 00:29:22,666
Huenda unaenda
nje ya mji kwa mapumziko,

473
00:29:22,699 --> 00:29:25,232
hivyo nataka tu kukutakia likizo
njema, na heri ya kuzaliwa.

474
00:29:25,266 --> 00:29:28,032
- Ni siku yako ya kuzaliwa, au sio?
- Kesho.

475
00:29:28,066 --> 00:29:30,165
Nimekutengenezea kitu.

476
00:29:32,699 --> 00:29:34,333
Hiki ni... Hiki ni nini?

477
00:29:34,366 --> 00:29:37,833
Ni mchanganuo wa
tathmini ya gharama

478
00:29:37,865 --> 00:29:39,665
wa matumizi yako ya kila wiki
ya Uber

479
00:29:39,699 --> 00:29:41,999
dhidi ya kumiliki gari lililotumika.

480
00:29:42,665 --> 00:29:44,633
Sawa...

481
00:29:44,665 --> 00:29:47,999
Najua. Ni kwamba tu,
inaonekana unapoteza pesa nyingi sana.

482
00:29:48,032 --> 00:29:51,798
Nilifanya utafiti kidogo,
na nikapata Toyota Corolla ya mwaka wa 2013,

483
00:29:51,833 --> 00:29:53,798
mjini,
ikiwa katika hali nzuri sana.

484
00:29:53,833 --> 00:29:56,731
Nilienda kwa muuzaji wa magari,
nikajadiliana masharti,

485
00:29:56,766 --> 00:30:00,232
na hutatoa pesa yoyote ya kwanza,
utalipa dola 150 tu kwa mwezi.

486
00:30:00,266 --> 00:30:03,165
Vance pia alikubali kuweka bima yako ya gari kwenye sera ya kampuni,

487
00:30:03,200 --> 00:30:04,798
hivyo hiyo ni bure.

488
00:30:04,833 --> 00:30:06,665
Hii ni, bila shaka,
ikiwa unataka kuifanya.

489
00:30:06,699 --> 00:30:07,699
Napenda tu
kupiga hesabu...

490
00:30:07,731 --> 00:30:09,066
Ee Mungu wangu!

491
00:30:09,099 --> 00:30:11,099
- Nadhani wewe...
- Ee Mungu wangu! Mwah!

492
00:30:11,133 --> 00:30:13,232
Asante.

493
00:30:16,032 --> 00:30:17,898
Kwaheri, Tessa.

494
00:30:22,898 --> 00:30:25,334
Hivyo, unaonaje?

495
00:30:25,366 --> 00:30:27,401
Sawa, unajua,

496
00:30:27,433 --> 00:30:29,066
ni, ee...

497
00:30:29,099 --> 00:30:30,865
ni mtindo wa Tessa kabisa.

498
00:30:30,898 --> 00:30:32,833
Nitachukulia hilo
kama sifa.

499
00:30:32,865 --> 00:30:34,965
Niko hapo juu.

500
00:30:38,200 --> 00:30:40,133
Dakota anaendeleaje?

501
00:30:40,165 --> 00:30:43,133
Ee, kwa kweli ninaangalia
utabiri wa nyota wa siku yako ya kuzaliwa.

502
00:30:43,165 --> 00:30:47,066
Hivyo kwanza kabisa,
unashiriki siku ya kuzaliwa na...

503
00:30:47,099 --> 00:30:49,598
- Joseph Stalin.
- Vyema.

504
00:30:50,266 --> 00:30:53,898
- Wewe ni mtu mwenye kiburi, mwenye msimamo dhabiti...
- Kama Stalin.

505
00:30:53,932 --> 00:30:57,066
Una hisia kali zaidi
kuliko inavyoonekana.

506
00:30:57,099 --> 00:31:01,032
Unaweza kuimarisha
uhusiano wa kimapenzi

507
00:31:01,066 --> 00:31:05,266
au kuanza uhusiano
na mwenzi aliyekomaa.

508
00:31:05,300 --> 00:31:07,401
Aliyekomaa.
Hiyo haisikiki kweli...

509
00:31:07,433 --> 00:31:09,833
Hapana, haisikiki hivyo.

510
00:31:09,865 --> 00:31:11,267
Aliondoka kwenda London.

511
00:31:11,300 --> 00:31:13,731
Je, umepata habari zake?

512
00:31:14,133 --> 00:31:16,300
Sijapata,
kwa sababu nilimzuia.

513
00:31:16,334 --> 00:31:18,632
Hiyo itafaa.

514
00:31:20,366 --> 00:31:22,665
Kwaheri.

515
00:31:59,334 --> 00:32:03,032
<i>Hapa ni nyumbani kwa nani?</i>

516
00:33:21,999 --> 00:33:24,134
<i>"Unaweza kunivuta kwenye moto,</i>

517
00:33:24,166 --> 00:33:26,099
<i>"unaweza kunivuta kwenye maji.</i>

518
00:33:26,134 --> 00:33:28,665
<i>"Unaweza kunivuta
kwenye mti wa kunyongea,</i>

519
00:33:28,699 --> 00:33:31,267
<i>unaweza kunivuta
kwenye kifo chochote."</i>

520
00:34:04,833 --> 00:34:07,699
Haya, tumefika.
Ninaweza kukuandalia maji ya kuoga

521
00:34:07,731 --> 00:34:09,201
kama ungependa kujihisi
huru zaidi.

522
00:34:09,233 --> 00:34:11,065
Ningependa hivyo.

523
00:34:11,101 --> 00:34:16,065
Nakumbuka wakati mimi na wewe
tulikuwa tukioga pamoja.

524
00:34:17,432 --> 00:34:19,367
Lahaula! Tessa?

525
00:34:19,400 --> 00:34:21,666
- Tessa.
- Mama yake Hardin.

526
00:34:21,699 --> 00:34:23,032
Hardin alisema ungekuwa
nje ya mji,

527
00:34:23,065 --> 00:34:24,932
Sikufikiria kwamba
ningekutana nawe!

528
00:34:24,965 --> 00:34:26,632
- Naam.
- Mungu wangu,

529
00:34:26,666 --> 00:34:28,400
Siwezi kuamini
jinsi ulivyo mrembo.

530
00:34:28,432 --> 00:34:30,266
Namaanisha, Hardin alisema wewe ndiye
msichana mrembo zaidi duniani,

531
00:34:30,300 --> 00:34:33,400
lakini kusema kweli, nilifikiri
ungekuwa umejaa chale,

532
00:34:33,432 --> 00:34:35,365
nywele za kijani,
na utoboji kwenye kiungo chako.

533
00:34:35,400 --> 00:34:36,932
- Kiungo gani?
- Mama.

534
00:34:36,965 --> 00:34:38,400
Usiwe na hamaki sana,
Hardin.

535
00:34:38,432 --> 00:34:40,134
Mimi na wewe tutakuwa
marafiki wa dhati.

536
00:34:40,166 --> 00:34:41,731
Je, unajali
nikitumia choo?

537
00:34:41,766 --> 00:34:43,300
Ndiyo, bila shaka.
Ni kwamba tu, mmh...

538
00:34:43,333 --> 00:34:45,632
Lo, jitazame!

539
00:34:47,067 --> 00:34:49,333
- Kwa nini upo hapa?
- Nilikuja kuchukua vitu vyangu vilivyobaki.

540
00:34:49,365 --> 00:34:51,134
- Ulipaswa kuwa London.
- Najua.

541
00:34:51,166 --> 00:34:52,898
Sikutaka kwenda bila
wewe, kwa hiyo akaja hapa.

542
00:34:52,932 --> 00:34:54,865
Kwa nini hukumwambia
kwamba tuliachana?

543
00:34:54,898 --> 00:34:56,898
Alifurahi sana
nilipomwambia kwanza,

544
00:34:56,932 --> 00:34:58,365
- Sikuweza kumharibia furaha yake.
- Hardin!

545
00:34:58,400 --> 00:35:00,067
Yeye ni mama yangu!
Nisingeweza kumwambia

546
00:35:00,101 --> 00:35:02,166
kuhusu lile dau la kipuuzi, sawa?
Unisamehe.

547
00:35:02,201 --> 00:35:06,699
Sitarajii ujifanye
kuwa bado tuko pamoja.

548
00:35:06,731 --> 00:35:09,067
- Ni sawa.
- Nini ni sawa?

549
00:35:09,101 --> 00:35:12,233
Nimesema ni sawa.
Nitashirikiana nawe.

550
00:35:12,266 --> 00:35:14,400
Asante, Tessa.
Asante sana.

551
00:35:14,432 --> 00:35:16,166
Asante kwa kifaa cha kusomea.

552
00:35:16,201 --> 00:35:18,333
Jamani! Heri ya siku ya kuzaliwa!

553
00:35:18,599 --> 00:35:20,865
- Je, ni siku yako ya kuzaliwa?
- Ndiyo, ni yenyewe.

554
00:35:20,898 --> 00:35:22,766
Kwa nini
hatusherehekei?

555
00:35:22,798 --> 00:35:25,766
Kwa sababu mimi... nilikuwa karibu
kuondoka mjini.

556
00:35:25,798 --> 00:35:28,166
- Hapana!
- Ndiyo, nitamwona mama yangu.

557
00:35:28,201 --> 00:35:32,865
Je, ninaweza kuwa mbinafsi na kukuomba
uabaki usiku mwingine?

558
00:35:33,333 --> 00:35:36,266
Vema, mama yangu
anatarajia...

559
00:35:36,300 --> 00:35:39,666
Hatujui ni lini
tutaonana tena.

560
00:35:39,699 --> 00:35:42,699
Ndiyo. Mimi, mmh, mimi...
Nadhani ninaweza kuondoka kesho.

561
00:35:42,731 --> 00:35:44,833
Vizuri sana, vizuri sana,
vizuri sana.

562
00:35:44,865 --> 00:35:48,798
Nitakuandalia keki ya siku ya kuzaliwa
ya nyumbani ambayo itakustaajabisha sana.

563
00:35:48,833 --> 00:35:50,166
Safi.

564
00:35:50,201 --> 00:35:51,766
Safi.

565
00:35:58,166 --> 00:36:00,101
Najua nina upendeleo
kwa sababu mimi ni mama yake,

566
00:36:00,134 --> 00:36:03,000
lakini je, hicho siyo tu kalio
dogo lenye kupendeza zaidi ambalo umewahi kuona?

567
00:36:03,034 --> 00:36:04,766
Loo, Mungu wangu, Mama, tafadhali.

568
00:36:04,798 --> 00:36:06,699
- Tulia.
- Ni kalio lenye kupendeza sana,

569
00:36:06,731 --> 00:36:08,699
Hardin.

570
00:36:08,731 --> 00:36:10,000
Sawa. Naam, ee,

571
00:36:10,034 --> 00:36:11,798
ninaona nyinyi wawili mnafurahia
sana wakati wenu,

572
00:36:11,833 --> 00:36:14,134
kwa hivyo nitasafisha
hapa kidogo,

573
00:36:14,166 --> 00:36:17,266
kisha...
nijiteketeze kwa moto.

574
00:36:17,300 --> 00:36:19,898
Kwa hivyo Hardin ameniambia wewe pia
unachukua masomo makuu ya Kiingereza.

575
00:36:19,932 --> 00:36:23,400
Mmh. Niko katika mchakato
wa kubadilisha kutoka uchumi.

576
00:36:23,432 --> 00:36:27,766
Kiukweli nimepata tu
fursa ya mafunzo kazini huko Vance Publishing.

577
00:36:27,798 --> 00:36:29,898
Vance, kama yule...
Christian Vance?

578
00:36:29,932 --> 00:36:32,034
Mmh.

579
00:36:33,134 --> 00:36:36,034
Hardin na mimi tuliishi na
Vance kwa miaka michache

580
00:36:36,067 --> 00:36:37,766
wakati mimi na Ken tulipoachana.

581
00:36:37,798 --> 00:36:39,898
- Kweli?
- Ndiyo.

582
00:36:40,599 --> 00:36:42,266
Hardin hakuwahi
kutaja hilo.

583
00:36:42,300 --> 00:36:43,798
Hakutaja nini?

584
00:36:43,833 --> 00:36:46,333
Hakuna kitu, mpenzi.
Mazungumzo ya wasichana tu.

585
00:37:15,034 --> 00:37:18,199
Nitaenda kuchukua blanketi
na kulala sakafuni.

586
00:37:18,233 --> 00:37:22,365
Hufikirii kwamba tunaweza
kushiriki kitanda na siyo...

587
00:37:22,400 --> 00:37:24,798
- Unajua.
- Unadhani?

588
00:37:24,833 --> 00:37:26,699
Naam, <i>ningependa</i> kufikiri

589
00:37:26,731 --> 00:37:30,034
kwamba sisi siyo
washamba kabisa.

590
00:37:30,666 --> 00:37:32,766
Sawa.

591
00:37:38,934 --> 00:37:40,798
Usiku mwema.

592
00:37:40,833 --> 00:37:42,934
Usiku mwema.

593
00:37:51,266 --> 00:37:53,365
Ee...

594
00:37:54,034 --> 00:37:57,731
Nitaondoka mapema
asubuhi

595
00:37:58,134 --> 00:38:00,266
ili... ili kuelekea nje ya mji.

596
00:38:04,731 --> 00:38:06,833
Sawa.

597
00:38:08,000 --> 00:38:10,967
Asante kwa
kukaa usiku huu.

598
00:38:12,134 --> 00:38:14,266
Asante kwa kunikaribisha.

599
00:38:21,000 --> 00:38:22,333
Samahani.

600
00:38:22,365 --> 00:38:25,067
Hapana. Hapana, ni...
Ni sawa tu.

601
00:38:40,900 --> 00:38:42,967
Hiyo inahisi vizuri.

602
00:38:43,900 --> 00:38:46,000
- Je, inahisi hivyo?
- Mm-hmm.

603
00:39:02,132 --> 00:39:05,132
- Je, ulikuwa na siku njema ya kuzaliwa?
- Ndiyo, nilikuwa nayo.

604
00:39:05,166 --> 00:39:08,867
Na asante tena
kwa ile... zawadi,

605
00:39:08,900 --> 00:39:10,266
ilikuwa yenye ufikiri sana.

606
00:39:10,300 --> 00:39:13,132
Niliipata nilipokuwa
nachukua vitu vyangu.

607
00:39:13,166 --> 00:39:15,233
Ninafurahi kwamba umeipenda.

608
00:39:16,099 --> 00:39:18,800
Ninaipenda sana.

609
00:39:27,532 --> 00:39:29,833
Nimepata gari.

610
00:39:30,233 --> 00:39:32,666
- Umepata gari?
- Mm-hmm.

611
00:39:33,300 --> 00:39:35,599
Ulipata gari gani?

612
00:39:39,166 --> 00:39:41,266
Moja nyeupe.

613
00:39:43,266 --> 00:39:45,599
Haya, heri ya siku ya kuzaliwa.

614
00:39:48,065 --> 00:39:50,166
Lala salama.

615
00:39:54,132 --> 00:39:56,233
Usiku mwema.

616
00:40:00,300 --> 00:40:02,900
- Usiku mwema.
- Usiku mwema.

617
00:40:04,800 --> 00:40:06,900
Usiku mwema.

618
00:40:18,300 --> 00:40:20,599
- Hardin.
- Ati?

619
00:40:21,000 --> 00:40:23,099
Hii haifanyi kazi.

620
00:40:24,365 --> 00:40:26,666
Kwa nini? Kuna nini?

621
00:40:27,934 --> 00:40:30,032
Hisi.

622
00:40:33,967 --> 00:40:36,065
Oh.

623
00:40:39,699 --> 00:40:41,800
Wewe?

624
00:40:46,032 --> 00:40:48,132
Oh.

625
00:41:06,934 --> 00:41:09,166
Hardin, tunapaswa kuacha.

626
00:41:09,934 --> 00:41:12,032
Sawa.

627
00:41:12,266 --> 00:41:13,400
Sekunde tatu
kisha tutaacha.

628
00:41:13,432 --> 00:41:15,733
- Mm.
- Mm-hmm.

629
00:41:17,733 --> 00:41:19,998
- Tatu...
- Tatu...

630
00:41:20,032 --> 00:41:22,099
- Mbili...
- Mbili...

631
00:41:22,833 --> 00:41:24,900
- Moja...
- Moja...

632
00:41:32,365 --> 00:41:34,800
- Sawa, sekunde kumi zaidi.
- Sawa.

633
00:41:34,833 --> 00:41:36,666
- Na kisha tutaacha.
- Sawa.

634
00:41:36,699 --> 00:41:38,800
- Ndiyo?
- Ndiyo.

635
00:41:43,065 --> 00:41:46,632
Je, utamwomba mama yako msamaha
kwa sisi kukuteka nyara jana usiku?

636
00:41:46,666 --> 00:41:48,733
Nitafanya hivyo.

637
00:41:49,932 --> 00:41:53,833
Siwezi kukuambia jinsi inavyomaanisha sana
kwangu kumwona Hardin akiwa hivi.

638
00:41:53,867 --> 00:41:55,998
Akiwa vipi?

639
00:41:56,032 --> 00:41:58,132
Mwenye furaha.

640
00:42:00,300 --> 00:42:01,632
Nini?

641
00:42:04,132 --> 00:42:06,233
- Kwaheri.
- Kwaheri.

642
00:42:32,965 --> 00:42:35,065
Gari zuri sana!

643
00:42:35,432 --> 00:42:37,965
- Vroom vroom!
- Noah, habari!

644
00:42:37,998 --> 00:42:39,300
- Habari!
- Ni vizuri kukuona!

645
00:42:39,333 --> 00:42:40,766
Ni vizuri kukuona pia.

646
00:42:40,800 --> 00:42:42,099
Mmm.

647
00:42:42,132 --> 00:42:44,233
Sawa...

648
00:42:44,898 --> 00:42:47,898
Mama yako aliniambia kuwa ulikuwa unakuja nyumbani leo, kwa hiyo nikaona nije kukusalimia.

649
00:42:47,932 --> 00:42:49,865
Je, alikuwa amekuweka kwenye namba za haraka

650
00:42:49,898 --> 00:42:51,733
sekunde ile niliyovuka mpaka wa kaunti?

651
00:42:51,766 --> 00:42:53,132
Namaanisha, unaweza kumlaumu?

652
00:42:53,166 --> 00:42:54,998
Anajua kitu kizuri anapokiona.

653
00:42:55,032 --> 00:42:56,632
- Kweli.
- Kweli.

654
00:42:56,666 --> 00:42:58,333
Eti, mwaka wa mwisho ukoje?

655
