Unanijua, kuvunja mioyo na kujitwalia sifa.

656
00:43:01,065 --> 00:43:03,666
- Huyo ni wewe.
- Sivyo? Ndiyo.

657
00:43:03,965 --> 00:43:06,132
Mama yako aliniambia kuhusu mafunzo ya kazi.

658
00:43:06,166 --> 00:43:08,400
- Hiyo ni nzuri sana.
- Asante. Ndiyo.

659
00:43:08,432 --> 00:43:10,898
Na kila kitu kiko sawa kuhusu jambo lile la baba yako.

660
00:43:10,932 --> 00:43:12,833
- Jambo gani la baba yangu?
- Nini?

661
00:43:12,865 --> 00:43:14,365
H-Hamna kitu. Hamna kitu.

662
00:43:14,400 --> 00:43:17,300
- Unamaanisha nini, hamna kitu?
- S-Sijui.

663
00:43:17,333 --> 00:43:20,032
- Nilidhani angekuwa...
- Ulidhani angefanya nini?

664
00:43:20,065 --> 00:43:22,766
Eeh...

665
00:43:23,400 --> 00:43:25,233
Unatania?

666
00:43:25,266 --> 00:43:27,865
- Kwa nini anakupigia simu?
- Samahani, Tess.

667
00:43:27,898 --> 00:43:29,699
<i>Samahani, nilikwama kazini.</i>

668
00:43:29,733 --> 00:43:31,266
- Je, ameshafika?
- Mama?

669
00:43:31,300 --> 00:43:33,400
- Carol, anajua!
- Anajua nini?!

670
00:43:33,432 --> 00:43:35,065
Oh! Tessa yuko na wewe.

671
00:43:35,099 --> 00:43:36,632
Natumai sikatishi jambo lolote.

672
00:43:36,666 --> 00:43:37,932
Kuna nini kinaendelea kuhusu Baba?!

673
00:43:37,965 --> 00:43:40,032
Sawa, hiyo haikuwa na adabu.

674
00:43:40,932 --> 00:43:42,400
Nakuuliza tu kuhusu Baba.

675
00:43:42,432 --> 00:43:43,898
<i>Haya.</i>

676
00:43:43,932 --> 00:43:45,365
Baba yako alitaka kukuona,

677
00:43:45,400 --> 00:43:47,699
lakini nilimfukuza.

678
00:43:47,733 --> 00:43:49,632
Kwa nini unakasirika sana hivi kuhusu jambo hili?

679
00:43:49,666 --> 00:43:51,365
Sikasiriki!

680
00:43:51,400 --> 00:43:53,400
Sielewi tu kwa nini ungeifanya hiyo kuwa siri.

681
00:43:53,432 --> 00:43:57,065
Na hukuwahi kunificha siri yoyote?

682
00:43:57,099 --> 00:44:00,199
<i>Kwa sababu naweza kufikiria moja kubwa, na Noah pia anaweza.</i>

683
00:44:00,233 --> 00:44:02,233
Nilifikiri tulishapita kikwazo hiki kidogo

684
00:44:02,266 --> 00:44:04,199
baada ya moyo wako kuvunjwa.

685
00:44:04,233 --> 00:44:06,099
<i>Lakini naweza kujua kwa sauti yako</i>

686
00:44:06,132 --> 00:44:07,865
<i>kwamba sivyo ilivyo.</i>

687
00:44:07,898 --> 00:44:10,199
Mvulana huyu si mzuri kwako, Teresa.

688
00:44:10,233 --> 00:44:12,965
- <i>Yeye ni kama baba yako tu.</i>
- Nakata simu.

689
00:44:12,998 --> 00:44:16,099
- <i>Hapana! Usidhubutu kunikatia simu!</i>
- Hili lilikuwa kosa.

690
00:44:16,132 --> 00:44:18,233
<i>Theresa? Theresa?</i>

691
00:44:18,998 --> 00:44:20,865
Nimeharibu kila kitu.

692
00:44:20,898 --> 00:44:22,666
Nimeharibu kila kitu, Carol.
Sijui nini kilitokea.

693
00:44:52,266 --> 00:44:54,233
Mama?

694
00:45:04,333 --> 00:45:05,666
Hapana!

695
00:45:05,699 --> 00:45:06,833
Mama?

696
00:45:06,865 --> 00:45:09,865
Hardin, rudi ghorofani sasa hivi!

697
00:45:11,666 --> 00:45:13,166
Hey. Hey, nipo hapa.

698
00:45:13,199 --> 00:45:15,300
Hey. Hey.

699
00:45:17,032 --> 00:45:18,898
Hey, ni sawa. Ni sawa.

700
00:45:20,166 --> 00:45:22,599
Ilikuwa ni ndoto mbaya tu.

701
00:45:34,798 --> 00:45:36,099
Habari za asubuhi.

702
00:45:36,132 --> 00:45:39,233
Kuna... um, kuna chai.
N... Jihudumie.

703
00:45:39,266 --> 00:45:41,365
Asante.

704
00:45:42,199 --> 00:45:44,065
Je, yuko sawa?

705
00:45:44,099 --> 00:45:46,333
- Hmm?
- Zile ndoto mbaya.

706
00:45:46,568 --> 00:45:48,865
Nilimsikia jana usiku.

707
00:45:48,898 --> 00:45:50,998
Um, amelala sasa hivi.

708
00:45:53,233 --> 00:45:56,266
Zimekuwa zikiendelea kwa muda gani?

709
00:45:57,699 --> 00:46:00,199
Uh, tangu alipokuwa na umri wa miaka minane.

710
00:46:01,898 --> 00:46:03,998
Um, yeye, uh, vizuri...

711
00:46:05,365 --> 00:46:07,833
Aliniambia...

712
00:46:07,865 --> 00:46:09,766
kuhusu usiku ule na kile alichokiona.

713
00:46:09,798 --> 00:46:11,898
Shambulio lile.

714
00:46:12,534 --> 00:46:16,300
Wow. Hajawahi kumwambia yeyote jambo hilo hapo awali.

715
00:46:18,266 --> 00:46:20,965
Pole sana kwa yale yaliyokupata.

716
00:46:20,998 --> 00:46:24,865
Nilitegemea tu angesahau kila kitu.

717
00:46:27,367 --> 00:46:31,300
Lakini zile ndoto mbaya zikaanza tena.

718
00:46:31,333 --> 00:46:33,798
Samahani.

719
00:46:33,833 --> 00:46:36,099
Na nilimpeleka kwa wataalamu wengi,

720
00:46:36,132 --> 00:46:38,300
lakini hakuna kilichoonekana kusaidia.

721
00:46:38,333 --> 00:46:42,798
Kisha akaanza
kujitibu kwa pombe.

722
00:46:42,833 --> 00:46:44,932
Lakini, hm...

723
00:46:47,266 --> 00:46:50,932
...aliniambia kuwa
jinamizi yaliisha

724
00:46:50,965 --> 00:46:52,965
alipoanza kukuona.

725
00:46:55,400 --> 00:46:57,699
Sikujua hilo.

726
00:47:01,166 --> 00:47:02,898
Naweza kuuliza...

727
00:47:02,932 --> 00:47:05,300
kwa nini mama yako
anamchukia kiasi hicho?

728
00:47:05,333 --> 00:47:07,731
Hm, Hardin ni mwanao...

729
00:47:08,333 --> 00:47:10,599
Ndiyo, na nampenda,

730
00:47:11,065 --> 00:47:14,300
lakini <i>si kwamba</i> hana
changamoto zake.

731
00:47:14,333 --> 00:47:18,833
Unaweza kuniambia.
Nini kilitokea kati yenu wawili?

732
00:47:21,099 --> 00:47:23,199
Alinidanganya.

733
00:47:23,798 --> 00:47:26,367
- Uongo mkubwa?
- Uongo mkubwa sana.

734
00:47:27,699 --> 00:47:29,798
Anajuta?

735
00:47:31,699 --> 00:47:33,233
Anajuta.

736
00:47:33,266 --> 00:47:36,766
Mnapiga soga kuhusu nini
ninyi wawili?

737
00:47:36,798 --> 00:47:38,798
Hakikisha
unapiga mswaki.

738
00:47:38,833 --> 00:47:41,898
Alikuwa akinisumbua sana
kuhusu kupiga mswaki.

739
00:47:41,932 --> 00:47:43,632
Mama, kwa ajili ya Mungu,

740
00:47:43,666 --> 00:47:45,300
bila shaka nitapiga
mswaki.

741
00:47:45,333 --> 00:47:47,400
Safi. Asubuhi njema!

742
00:47:47,434 --> 00:47:50,666
Asubuhi njema. Asante.

743
00:47:51,300 --> 00:47:53,367
Nampenda mama yako.

744
00:47:54,032 --> 00:47:56,132
Yuko sawa.

745
00:47:58,932 --> 00:48:01,032
Heri ya siku ya kuzaliwa iliyopita.

746
00:48:01,534 --> 00:48:03,998
Lakini tayari
ulishanipa zawadi.

747
00:48:04,032 --> 00:48:06,032
Kweli, lakini ilibidi
upekuepekue

748
00:48:06,065 --> 00:48:07,998
na kuifungua bila mimi,
hivyo kuninyima

749
00:48:08,032 --> 00:48:10,998
raha ya kukuona
ukishangazwa na hiyo zawadi.

750
00:48:11,032 --> 00:48:13,132
Kwa hiyo...

751
00:48:14,199 --> 00:48:16,300
"Siku kamilifu ya Tessa."

752
00:48:17,833 --> 00:48:19,898
Siku yangu kamilifu ni ipi?

753
00:48:19,932 --> 00:48:21,865
Naam, hilo ni juu yako kuamua.

754
00:48:21,898 --> 00:48:24,065
Lolote utakalo au utamani,

755
00:48:24,099 --> 00:48:28,898
Nitakubali bila
kejeli au hasira za kitoto.

756
00:48:28,932 --> 00:48:32,233
Muda wako unaanza baada ya tatu,
mbili, moja.

757
00:48:34,199 --> 00:48:36,233
Si hapa ni pazuri?

758
00:48:36,266 --> 00:48:39,400
Daima nilitaka
kwenda kuteleza kwenye barafu.

759
00:48:39,434 --> 00:48:42,132
Ndiyo, ni... safi.
Napenda...

760
00:48:42,166 --> 00:48:44,300
Ah! Ah...

761
00:48:44,333 --> 00:48:46,367
- Uko sawa?
- Ndiyo.

762
00:48:46,400 --> 00:48:48,065
Nimepata kutu kidogo tu.

763
00:48:48,099 --> 00:48:49,898
Lini ilikuwa mara yako ya mwisho
kuteleza?

764
00:48:49,932 --> 00:48:52,166
Sijawahi kuteleza hapo awali.

765
00:48:52,199 --> 00:48:53,833
Unataka nikuletée
kifaa cha kukusaidia kutembea?

766
00:48:53,865 --> 00:48:56,032
Unafanya vizuri sana.

767
00:48:56,065 --> 00:48:58,300
Hapana kabisa!

768
00:48:58,333 --> 00:49:02,065
Je, uko... Oh, ni sawa. Ni... ni sawa.

769
00:49:02,099 --> 00:49:04,201
Whoo.

770
00:49:04,731 --> 00:49:07,032
- Uko sawa?
- Naam.

771
00:49:07,367 --> 00:49:09,666
Unataka tuache?

772
00:49:09,898 --> 00:49:12,132
Hapana.
Tuko hapa ili...

773
00:49:13,099 --> 00:49:16,065
Unhh! Aaah!

774
00:49:16,099 --> 00:49:18,898
Hardin?
Nina wazo bora zaidi.

775
00:49:18,932 --> 00:49:21,266
Jinyooshe katika
Pozi la Mtoto,

776
00:49:21,300 --> 00:49:25,333
na uruhusu mkazo wa siku
uayeyuke tu.

777
00:49:25,367 --> 00:49:27,898
Si pozi hili
linaloyeyusha mkazo huu,

778
00:49:27,932 --> 00:49:29,932
- ni joto hili kali.
- Shh!

779
00:49:29,965 --> 00:49:32,666
- Je, kuna kiyoyozi chochote?
- Hii ni yoga ya joto.

780
00:49:32,699 --> 00:49:35,731
Kutoka Pozi la Mtoto,
inua, na usukume nyuma polepole

781
00:49:35,766 --> 00:49:38,798
hadi Pozi la Mbwa Anayetazama Chini.

782
00:49:38,833 --> 00:49:40,266
Je, kuna mtu alishawahi kukuambia

783
00:49:40,300 --> 00:49:42,898
una makalio ya kustaajabisha zaidi?

784
00:49:42,932 --> 00:49:44,666
Acha.

785
00:49:44,699 --> 00:49:47,666
...na kisha ingia polepole kwenye
<i>salamba sarvangasana.</i>

786
00:49:47,699 --> 00:49:50,201
Samahani,
je, hii ni yoga ya wanaoanza?

787
00:49:50,233 --> 00:49:54,266
Hiyo ilikuwa saa nne na nusu.
Hii ni acro-yoga.

788
00:49:55,932 --> 00:49:59,965
...na kisha zainue
juu kuelekea kwenye dari.

789
00:49:59,998 --> 00:50:02,099
Vuteni pumzi pamoja.

790
00:50:04,965 --> 00:50:08,099
Vuta pumzi, inua mikono yako juu ya kichwa.

791
00:50:10,065 --> 00:50:12,833
Na unapohema,
inamia mbele.

792
00:50:12,865 --> 00:50:16,998
Ruhusu uzito wa mwenzako ukuegemee.

793
00:50:17,032 --> 00:50:19,699
Vuta pumzi polepole na
panua miguu yako na...

794
00:50:19,731 --> 00:50:21,833
zaidi... vuta pumzi...

795
00:50:23,233 --> 00:50:24,932
kidogo zaidi...

796
00:50:24,965 --> 00:50:28,731
na ukiweza,
panua miguu yako zaidi.

797
00:50:35,400 --> 00:50:38,632
Je, yoga inapaswa
kumsisimua mtu kimapenzi?

798
00:50:41,065 --> 00:50:43,333
Je, umesisimka?

799
00:50:43,367 --> 00:50:44,898
Mm-hmm.

800
00:50:44,932 --> 00:50:46,865
- Basi tunaweza kuondoka?
- Mm-hmm.

801
00:50:46,898 --> 00:50:49,998
- Sasa? Twende.
- Mm-hmm. Mm-hmm.

802
00:50:50,865 --> 00:50:52,965
Jasho! Nina jasho!

803
00:50:53,266 --> 00:50:56,101
Subiri! Nipe dakika
tano tu, sawa?

804
00:50:56,134 --> 00:50:58,965
Nahitaji tu kupata...

805
00:51:04,134 --> 00:51:06,233
Mungu wangu. Hardin.

806
00:51:09,798 --> 00:51:13,766
Hebu tuvitoe hivi.

807
00:51:17,699 --> 00:51:19,365
Sawa, tunapiga hatua fulani!

808
00:51:57,134 --> 00:51:59,201
Ohoo, lahaula!

809
00:52:55,666 --> 00:52:57,898
Ni bosi wangu,
lazima nipokee hii.

810
00:52:57,932 --> 00:53:00,034
Una uhakika?

811
00:53:00,467 --> 00:53:03,233
Habari! Kimberly,
kuna shida gani?

812
00:53:05,201 --> 00:53:07,333
Oi, hapana. Tunawezaje kusaidia?

813
00:53:08,034 --> 00:53:09,166
Hmm.

814
00:53:09,201 --> 00:53:10,632
Habari.

815
00:53:10,666 --> 00:53:12,967
Hamjui ni kwa kiasi gani

816
00:53:13,000 --> 00:53:14,166
ninyi wawili mmetuokoa sasa hivi.

817
00:53:14,201 --> 00:53:15,833
Mungu wangu, maskini Vance
ameweza kupata ugonjwa huu

818
00:53:15,865 --> 00:53:17,898
na anatapika
kila mahali.

819
00:53:17,932 --> 00:53:19,833
Hakuna shida.

820
00:53:19,865 --> 00:53:23,000
Sawa, wewe ni nani na
umemfanya nini Hardin?

821
00:53:23,034 --> 00:53:25,632
Ni sehemu ya zawadi yangu ya kuzaliwa.
Nitakuambia baadaye.

822
00:53:25,666 --> 00:53:28,166
Ohoo! Nimechelewa sana.

823
00:53:28,201 --> 00:53:31,967
Nitarejea baada ya saa chache,
sawa? Uko mikononi salama.

824
00:53:32,000 --> 00:53:34,865
- Kwaheri.
- Asante.

825
00:53:37,934 --> 00:53:40,034
Habari.

826
00:53:40,067 --> 00:53:44,034
Um, basi, tuna alasiri
nzima tukiwa pamoja.

827
00:53:44,067 --> 00:53:47,300
- Kuna chochote unachotaka kufanya?
- Hapana.

828
00:53:47,333 --> 00:53:49,934
Ningeweza kutuletea kalamu za rangi
na tunaweza kuchora!

829
00:53:49,967 --> 00:53:51,766
Sipendi kuchora.

830
00:53:51,798 --> 00:53:53,898
Hupendi? Una njaa?

831
00:53:55,833 --> 00:53:57,934
Hapana.

832
00:54:07,766 --> 00:54:10,798
Unataka kuniambia
kuhusu treni zako?

833
00:54:13,666 --> 00:54:15,865
Sawa, sitaki
kuzisikia hata hivyo.

834
00:54:15,900 --> 00:54:17,865
Ni alama gani hizo
kwenye mkono wako?

835
00:54:17,900 --> 00:54:19,365
Tatoo zangu.

836
00:54:19,400 --> 00:54:22,134
- Kwa nini unazo?
- Kwa sababu nazipenda.

837
00:54:22,166 --> 00:54:23,865
Je, watu hawafikirii
kuwa inaonekana ya ajabu?

838
00:54:23,900 --> 00:54:25,798
Sijali hata kidogo
kile watu wanachofikiria.

839
00:54:25,833 --> 00:54:27,934
Ni watu gani ambao
huwajali hata kidogo?

840
00:54:27,967 --> 00:54:30,233
- Ohoo, lahaula. Usiseme neno hilo.
- Lahaula.

841
00:54:30,266 --> 00:54:32,034
Laana. Mavi.

842
00:54:32,067 --> 00:54:34,134
Laana kabisa. Mavi...

843
00:54:34,967 --> 00:54:37,067
- Habari. Basi...
- Habari!

844
00:54:37,300 --> 00:54:39,300
kwa kweli ana njaa sasa.
Tunahitaji kumletea...

845
00:54:39,333 --> 00:54:40,798
Laana. Mavi.

846
00:54:40,833 --> 00:54:42,199
Hmm, naweza kwenda ukitaka.

847
00:54:42,233 --> 00:54:43,967
- Au unaweza kwenda wewe.
- Hapana, ni sawa.

848
00:54:44,000 --> 00:54:45,900
- Nitachukua sandwichi kwa ajili yetu.
- Safi sana.

849
00:54:45,934 --> 00:54:48,266
- Asante sana.
- Haya! Sawa!

850
00:54:48,300 --> 00:54:49,632
- Tutaonana baadaye. Kwaheri.
- Sawa, kwaheri!

851
00:54:49,666 --> 00:54:52,101
Mavi. Laana. Mavi.

852
00:54:54,699 --> 00:54:56,798
Endelea.

853
00:54:59,101 --> 00:55:01,699
Hapa,
naweza kuvichukua hivyo sasa.

854
00:55:01,967 --> 00:55:04,333
Unajua, kwa kweli
aye hufanya uwe bora zaidi.

855
00:55:04,365 --> 00:55:06,867
Je, ni dhahiri kiasi hicho?

856
00:55:06,900 --> 00:55:08,867
Uwe na likizo njema.

857
00:55:08,900 --> 00:55:11,000
Nawe pia.

858
00:55:12,400 --> 00:55:13,766
Tutaonana, rafiki.

859
00:55:13,798 --> 00:55:15,900
Tutaonana, rafiki.

860
00:55:22,365 --> 00:55:24,034
Uko tayari?

861
00:55:24,067 --> 00:55:27,132
Ndiyo. Hmm, sisi ndio
wa mwisho hapa,

862
00:55:27,166 --> 00:55:29,400
kwa hiyo inabidi tu
nitege king'ora.

863
00:55:29,432 --> 00:55:31,731
Krismasi Njema.

864
00:55:33,432 --> 00:55:36,034
Krismasi ni wiki ijayo.

865
00:55:38,034 --> 00:55:41,800
Sijawahi kuwa mtu
wa kufuata sheria.

866
00:55:48,132 --> 00:55:50,233
Inasema "Chochote roho zetu
zimeumbwa kwacho..."

867
00:55:50,266 --> 00:55:52,967
"Yake na yangu
ni sawa."

868
00:55:57,000 --> 00:55:59,099
Kuna nini?

869
00:56:02,800 --> 00:56:08,166
Sikufikiri kama ningekuona wakati wa
likizo, hivyo sikukununulia chochote.

870
00:56:08,199 --> 00:56:11,065
Kuna kitu chochote
unachotaka?

871
00:56:13,900 --> 00:56:15,934
Nafasi nyingine?

872
00:56:18,599 --> 00:56:21,266
Je, unaahidi kuwa na tabia
kama hii kila siku?

873
00:56:21,300 --> 00:56:23,599
Hapana.

874
00:56:25,900 --> 00:56:28,000
Lakini nitajaribu.

875
00:56:35,766 --> 00:56:37,867
Vyovyote itakavyogharimu.

876
00:57:05,266 --> 00:57:08,132
Hatuwezi kufanya hivi hapa.
Vipi kama mtu akiingia?

877
00:57:08,166 --> 00:57:11,300
Hujambooo?
Kuna mtu hapa?

878
00:57:11,900 --> 00:57:13,900
Kuna yeyote?!

879
00:57:13,934 --> 00:57:18,699
Una jibu kwa
kila kitu, sivyo?

880
00:57:31,998 --> 00:57:33,766
Ni bandia.

881
00:57:33,800 --> 00:57:35,867
Laana.

882
00:59:03,365 --> 00:59:06,365
Hakuna mwingine
kwa ajili yangu, Tessa.

883
00:59:06,400 --> 00:59:08,699
Hakuna mmoja.

884
00:59:12,733 --> 00:59:14,833
Nakupenda.

885
00:59:15,132 --> 00:59:17,867
Nakupenda pia.

886
00:59:18,898 --> 00:59:24,099
Usiseme "pia." Inasikika kana kwamba
unakubaliana nami.

887
00:59:25,032 --> 00:59:27,132
Nakupenda, Hardin.

888
00:59:59,400 --> 01:00:00,998
<i>Trish.</i>

889
01:00:01,032 --> 01:00:02,199
Ndiyo, ni Ken.

890
01:00:02,233 --> 01:00:04,333
Huu ni mshangao.

891
01:00:04,365 --> 01:00:07,599
Basi sikiliza, um,
mke wangu Karen na mimi

892
01:00:08,865 --> 01:00:12,333
tunakaribisha watu
kwa ajili ya Krismasi, na...

893
01:00:12,365 --> 01:00:15,898
tungependa kama wewe na
Hardin na Tessa mngeweza kujiunga nasi.

894
01:00:15,932 --> 01:00:20,233
Naam, ninaondoka kwenda London
leo, lakini, um...

895
01:00:20,266 --> 01:00:22,632
ndege haiondoki
hadi jioni ya leo,

896
01:00:22,666 --> 01:00:24,800
kwa hiyo nafikiri
tunaweza kupita.

897
01:00:24,833 --> 01:00:26,400
Ingekuwa na maana kubwa sana kwangu.

898
01:00:26,432 --> 01:00:29,833
Nadhani tutaonana baadaye,
basi.

899
01:00:29,865 --> 01:00:32,166
Heri ya Krismasi, Trish.

900
01:00:34,432 --> 01:00:35,932
- Ndiyo?
- Ndiyo.

901
01:00:35,965 --> 01:00:37,065
- Ndiyo?
- Ndiyo.

902
01:00:37,099 --> 01:00:39,233
Lo! Ninajivunia sana kwa ajili yako.

903
01:00:39,666 --> 01:00:41,965
Siwezi kusubiri kukutana naye.

904
01:01:05,432 --> 01:01:07,733
Hii ni <i>nyumba yake?</i>

905
01:01:08,798 --> 01:01:11,132
- Nilikuambia.
- Jamani,

906
01:01:11,166 --> 01:01:13,865
Sikufikiria
kuwa ni <i>kubwa hivi</i>.

907
01:01:13,898 --> 01:01:15,865
Mama, hatulazimiki
kufanya hivi.

908
01:01:15,898 --> 01:01:20,132
Sikiliza, mara ya mwisho nilipomwona
baba yako ilikuwa miaka kumi iliyopita.

909
01:01:20,166 --> 01:01:22,365
Ni wakati. Haya.

910
01:01:26,733 --> 01:01:28,365
- Habari. Karen?
- Ndiyo, habari.

911
01:01:28,400 --> 01:01:29,798
Asante kwa kutukaribisha.

912
01:02:03,833 --> 01:02:06,266
Haya, karibuni.
Heri ya Krismasi.

913
01:02:24,400 --> 01:02:27,632
Huyu mnyenyekevu,
hapa sasa hivi,

914
01:02:28,099 --> 01:02:30,965
ameandika kwa ushirikiano
tafsiri mpya

915
01:02:30,998 --> 01:02:32,798
ya <i>Taming of the Shrew</i>

916
01:02:32,833 --> 01:02:34,333
na mkuu wa
idara ya Kiingereza.

917
01:02:34,365 --> 01:02:36,766
Sio jambo kubwa.

918
01:02:36,798 --> 01:02:38,365
<i>Ni</i> jambo kubwa!

919
01:02:48,065 --> 01:02:49,666
...aliongoza hiyo kwa ukamilifu.

920
01:02:49,699 --> 01:02:52,166
Sehemu hiyo ya tatu
ilinitoa machozi.

921
01:02:52,199 --> 01:02:54,032
Tuliona mara mbili.

922
01:03:24,666 --> 01:03:26,266
<i>Uber itafika hapa hivi karibuni</i>

923
01:03:26,300 --> 01:03:28,199
- baada ya dakika tano.
- Oh!

924
01:03:28,233 --> 01:03:30,099
Vema, ninafurahi
kwamba umepita.

925
01:03:30,132 --> 01:03:31,833
Mimi pia.

926
01:03:31,865 --> 01:03:33,798
Chakula cha jioni
kitakuwa tayari hivi karibuni.

927
01:03:33,833 --> 01:03:36,333
Sawa, natumai kila mtu
ana hamu kubwa ya kula.

928
01:03:36,367 --> 01:03:38,400
- Kabisa!
- Karen ni mpishi stadi sana.

929
01:03:38,434 --> 01:03:40,367
Ndiyo, ni kweli.

930
01:03:40,400 --> 01:03:42,132
Ulienda wapi?

931
01:03:42,166 --> 01:03:43,865
Kwa matembezi tu.

932
01:03:43,898 --> 01:03:45,666
Hivyo Trish,
nasikia kwamba

933
01:03:45,699 --> 01:03:47,065
hii ni mara yako ya kwanza
nchini Marekani?

934
01:03:47,099 --> 01:03:49,065
- Ndiyo, ni kweli.
- Na unaipendaje?

935
01:03:49,099 --> 01:03:51,199
Kuna mengi ya kuona.

936
01:03:51,233 --> 01:03:54,300
Imepoteza mvuto wake kiasi,
ukiniuliza mimi.

937
01:03:54,333 --> 01:03:57,632
Nitafurahi kurudi nyumbani
nikishahitimu.

938
01:03:57,666 --> 01:04:00,266
Unarudi Uingereza
baada ya kuhitimu?

939
01:04:00,300 --> 01:04:02,599
Ndiyo, bila shaka.

940
01:04:02,833 --> 01:04:05,699
Trish, nikuletee
gilasi nyingine kabla hujatuacha?

941
01:04:05,731 --> 01:04:07,300
Hapana. Lakini kilikuwa kizuri.
Asante.

942
01:04:07,333 --> 01:04:08,932
Ninafurahi sana kwamba umekipenda.

943
01:04:08,965 --> 01:04:10,699
Tulikipata nchini Ugiriki
kwenye fungate yetu.

944
01:04:10,731 --> 01:04:12,865
Mimi nilibaki na Pellegrino.

945
01:04:12,898 --> 01:04:16,032
Tulikaa katika
vila hii ya kupendeza.

946
01:04:16,333 --> 01:04:19,666
Je, ulijua kwamba
fukwe za Santorini

947
01:04:19,699 --> 01:04:21,833
zimeundwa kwa
kokoto za volkano,

948
01:04:21,865 --> 01:04:24,998
hivyo hakuna mchanga
wa kufanya maji yawe machafu.

949
01:04:25,032 --> 01:04:27,233
Hivyo ni safi kabisa...

950
01:04:27,266 --> 01:04:29,898
- Una tatizo gani wewe?
- Hardin.

951
01:04:29,932 --> 01:04:32,166
- Samahani?
- Tazama suruali yako ya kipumbavu.

952
01:04:32,199 --> 01:04:33,798
Samahani, Mama,
lakini kwa dhati,

953
01:04:33,833 --> 01:04:35,632
je, huna hisia
zovyote vile?

954
01:04:35,666 --> 01:04:38,032
Unaropoka tu bila adabu

955
01:04:38,065 --> 01:04:40,132
bila kujali
maisha uliyoyaharibu.

956
01:04:40,166 --> 01:04:43,865
P-Pengine tunaweza kupata
pahali pa faragha zaidi

957
01:04:43,898 --> 01:04:46,965
- ili kuwa na mazungumzo haya.
- Bila shaka.

958
01:04:46,998 --> 01:04:49,599
Ni Bill Gates.

959
01:04:51,032 --> 01:04:53,766
Sawa, basi, ni wazi kuwa
ughadhibika sana nami,

960
01:04:53,798 --> 01:04:56,166
hivyo endelea na useme
kilicho akilini mwako.

961
01:04:56,199 --> 01:04:58,065
Mbona hata
ulitualika hapa?

962
01:04:58,099 --> 01:05:00,032
Niliwaalika hapa
kwa sababu ninyi ni familia yangu.

963
01:05:00,065 --> 01:05:02,233
Sisi si familia yako.
<i>Tulikuwa</i> familia yako.

964
01:05:02,266 --> 01:05:04,898
- Ulikimbia na kujibadilisha...
- Hardin, nilidhani tulishayavuka haya.

965
01:05:04,932 --> 01:05:07,400
Hatukuyavuka. Tulipaswa
tuyavuke vipi?

966
01:05:07,434 --> 01:05:09,898
Hujakubali makosa
yako kwa lolote!

967
01:05:09,932 --> 01:05:12,032
Hatua zako kumi na mbili...
kufanya marekebisho.

968
01:05:12,065 --> 01:05:14,965
Marekebisho ya Mama yako wapi?
Mama, umeshapata marekebisho yako bado?

969
01:05:14,998 --> 01:05:16,666
Ungetaka
nifanye nini?

970
01:05:16,699 --> 01:05:18,065
Hufikirii kwamba
nimemezwa na hatia?

971
01:05:18,099 --> 01:05:20,699
Nilijua usiku ule
kwamba ilibidi niondoke.

972
01:05:20,731 --> 01:05:22,898
Hapana! Baada ya usiku ule
ilibidi <i>ubaki!</i>

973
01:05:22,932 --> 01:05:25,166
Na hukubaki!
Usiku ule ulitokea <i>kwa sababu</i> yako!

974
01:05:25,199 --> 01:05:27,632
Ndiyo! Na nimekuwa nikiteswa
nayo kwa miaka kumi iliyopita!

975
01:05:27,666 --> 01:05:30,132
Inakutesa?!
Niliona kabisa ikitokea,

976
01:05:30,166 --> 01:05:33,032
ewe mwanaharamu!

977
01:05:38,333 --> 01:05:40,666
Nisamehe, Mama.

978
01:05:40,699 --> 01:05:42,766
<i>Ilibidi</i> nifanye hivyo.

979
01:05:43,333 --> 01:05:46,865
Hapana, subiri. Huhitaji kuchukua teksi.
Naweza kukupeleka.

980
01:05:46,898 --> 01:05:49,201
Baada ya mambo ya hovyo
uliyoyafanya sasa hivi?

981
01:05:49,233 --> 01:05:51,898
Bila kusahau
kwamba umelewa.

982
01:05:51,932 --> 01:05:53,998
Sikiliza, nisamehe
kwamba siko kama wewe.

983
01:05:54,032 --> 01:05:56,898
Unaweza kusahau kila kitu
alichofanya, lakini mimi siwezi.

984
01:05:56,932 --> 01:05:59,333
Sijasahau chochote.

985
01:05:59,367 --> 01:06:03,865
<i>Nimechagua</i> kumsamehe
ili <i>mimi</i> niweze kuendelea.

986
01:06:04,766 --> 01:06:08,400
Hardin, vinyongo kama hivi
vitakuangamiza.

987
01:06:08,434 --> 01:06:13,132
Na vitamwangamiza Tessa
pamoja nawe.

988
01:06:32,400 --> 01:06:35,099
Naenda kutembea.

989
01:06:45,932 --> 01:06:48,266
Laana!

990
01:07:14,134 --> 01:07:16,932
Hardin.

991
01:07:19,400 --> 01:07:21,666
Hardin.

992
01:07:21,699 --> 01:07:23,266
Hardin!

993
01:08:02,998 --> 01:08:05,101
Zuia hapo, tafadhali!

994
01:08:06,101 --> 01:08:08,201
Oh.

995
01:08:10,300 --> 01:08:14,400
Na nilidhani nilikuwa mchoyo pekee
niliyekuwa nikifanya kazi siku baada ya Krismasi.

996
01:08:14,432 --> 01:08:17,166
Inabidi tuache
kukutana hivi.

997
01:08:17,201 --> 01:08:21,266
Upo sahihi. Nitafanya amri ya kuzuia
iandaliwe mara moja.

998
01:08:21,300 --> 01:08:22,998
Krismasi yako ilikuwaje?

999
01:08:23,032 --> 01:08:25,134
Ilikuwa tulivu. Yako?

1000
01:08:25,898 --> 01:08:27,998
Ilikuwa na mambo mengi.

1001
01:08:28,234 --> 01:08:30,833
Hilo ni jibu lenye maana nzito.

1002
01:08:33,365 --> 01:08:36,166
Basi, ningependa kusikia zaidi
kuhusu Krismasi yako iliyojaa matukio,

1003
01:08:36,201 --> 01:08:37,966
basi... chakula cha mchana?

1004
01:08:37,998 --> 01:08:39,300
Agizo la chakula la mtandaoni. Mimi nitalipa.

1005
01:08:39,333 --> 01:08:41,300
Ninawezaje kukataa?

1006
01:08:41,333 --> 01:08:43,932
Safi. Nitakutumia baadhi ya
orodha za vyakula kwa barua pepe.

1007
01:08:43,966 --> 01:08:46,833
Najua,
ni uungwana mkubwa kutoka kwangu.

1008
01:08:50,333 --> 01:08:55,100
Nilidhani mambo yalikuwa
yakiimarika, lakini...

1009
01:08:55,134 --> 01:08:59,033
ni wazi kwamba bado ana
mambo mengi ya kushughulikia.

1010
01:08:59,067 --> 01:09:02,201
Na ninamhurumia sana...

1011
01:09:02,234 --> 01:09:04,832
na sijui
jinsi ya kurekebisha.

1012
01:09:04,865 --> 01:09:07,167
Basi, acha nikuulize hili.

1013
01:09:08,201 --> 01:09:10,631
Je, unampenda?

1014
01:09:11,365 --> 01:09:14,899
- Nampenda.
- Basi una tatizo.

1015
01:09:16,932 --> 01:09:18,765
Hayo ndiyo
maneno yako ya hekima?

1016
01:09:18,798 --> 01:09:21,167
Hebu sikia, sijawahi kusema nina
maneno yoyote ya hekima.

1017
01:09:21,201 --> 01:09:26,698
Hapana, ulitaka tu kujua
kama kweli nampenda.

1018
01:09:26,731 --> 01:09:29,033
Napaswa kurudi kazini.

1019
01:09:30,399 --> 01:09:33,100
Asante kwa chakula cha mchana.
Wakati ujao ni juu yangu.

1020
01:09:33,134 --> 01:09:36,399
Sidhani kama
kutakuwa na wakati ujao.

1021
01:09:36,432 --> 01:09:37,932
Inauma.

1022
01:09:37,966 --> 01:09:40,666
Hapana, si hivyo,
niamini.

1023
01:09:40,698 --> 01:09:42,365
Nahamia Seattle.

1024
01:09:42,399 --> 01:09:45,300
Vance alinipa nafasi ya Mkuu wa
Fedha katika ofisi mpya.

1025
01:09:45,332 --> 01:09:47,201
Ee Mungu wangu.
Trevor, hiyo inapendeza sana.

1026
01:09:47,234 --> 01:09:49,167
Asante.

1027
01:09:49,201 --> 01:09:51,332
Basi, unajua,
siondoki kesho.

1028
01:09:51,365 --> 01:09:53,134
Bado tunaweza... hiyo ni...

1029
01:09:53,167 --> 01:09:55,932
Hapana, huo ni upuuzi.

1030
01:10:04,134 --> 01:10:06,233
Tessa.

1031
01:10:06,934 --> 01:10:12,365
Dada yangu amepambana
na uraibu maisha yake yote.

1032
01:10:12,399 --> 01:10:14,666
Jambo hili kati
yako na Hardin...

1033
01:10:14,698 --> 01:10:16,934
halitaisha vizuri.

1034
01:10:20,432 --> 01:10:22,731
Basi, umekosea.

1035
01:10:59,934 --> 01:11:02,332
Hii ni bora zaidi
hata hivyo.

1036
01:11:15,265 --> 01:11:19,300
Hutawahi nionyesha unachoandika
humo, au siyo?

1037
01:11:19,332 --> 01:11:21,631
Labda... siku moja.

1038
01:11:29,067 --> 01:11:31,000
Hutaki kuona
ni nani huyo?

1039
01:11:31,033 --> 01:11:33,134
Najua ni nani.

1040
01:11:33,166 --> 01:11:34,765
Ni Steph.

1041
01:11:34,798 --> 01:11:39,000
Klabu ya wanafunzi ina
sherehe ya mkesha wa Mwaka Mpya.

1042
01:11:39,033 --> 01:11:41,132
Sawa.

1043
01:11:41,365 --> 01:11:43,033
Unataka kwenda?

1044
01:11:43,067 --> 01:11:46,731
Hapana. Sitaki
kukuacha hapa peke yako.

1045
01:11:47,399 --> 01:11:49,731
Nisingekuwa peke yangu.

1046
01:11:49,765 --> 01:11:51,867
Ningeenda na wewe.

1047
01:11:53,067 --> 01:11:56,199
Samahani, mimi... nilifikiri tu
baada ya kila kilichotokea

1048
01:11:56,233 --> 01:11:58,067
- kwamba usingetaka...
- Sawaogopi.

1049
01:11:58,100 --> 01:12:00,265
Isitoshe, kama mambo
yakienda vibaya kwangu,

1050
01:12:00,300 --> 01:12:03,631
basi tunaweza tu
kubaki ndani mwaka ujao.

1051
01:12:13,100 --> 01:12:15,199
Hiyo ilikuwa ya nini?

1052
01:12:18,033 --> 01:12:21,631
Nimependa tu
jinsi ulivyosema "mwaka ujao."

1053
01:12:27,365 --> 01:12:28,899
Halo?

1054
01:12:28,934 --> 01:12:30,332
Tessa, kwa nini haupo
ofisini?

1055
01:12:30,365 --> 01:12:32,033
Naam, ndiyo, mimi...
nilifikiri ilikuwa...

1056
01:12:32,067 --> 01:12:33,399
Natania tu.
Heri ya Mwaka Mpya.

1057
01:12:33,432 --> 01:12:35,867
Ndiyo!

1058
01:12:35,899 --> 01:12:37,631
Umenipata.

1059
01:12:37,666 --> 01:12:39,300
<i>Nitaenda moja kwa moja kwenye mada.</i>

1060
01:12:39,332 --> 01:12:41,265
Tulichagua muswada
ulioopendekeza,

1061
01:12:41,300 --> 01:12:43,332
na umeuzwa leo
katika ushindani mkubwa wa bei.

1062
01:12:43,365 --> 01:12:46,233
Wow, hiyo ni...
hiyo ni ya kustaajabisha.

1063
01:12:46,265 --> 01:12:48,033
<i>Sikiliza, tulikuwa
tuajiri mtu</i>

1064
01:12:48,065 --> 01:12:49,765
<i>wa kushughulikia mawasilisho ya kidijitali
huko Seattle, lakini...</i>

1065
01:12:49,800 --> 01:12:52,199
wewe ni bora kuliko yeyote
niliyemhoji.

1066
01:12:52,233 --> 01:12:54,631
<i>Nitalipia ada yako ya masomo,
gharama za maisha, mradi tu uhamie huku.</i>

1067
01:12:54,666 --> 01:12:58,332
Ni wazi, Hardin anakaribishwa
kuungana nawe.

1068
01:12:58,365 --> 01:12:59,666
Wow, hiyo...

1069
01:12:59,698 --> 01:13:02,666
uh, hiyo inasikika
kustaajabisha sana.

1070
01:13:03,599 --> 01:13:07,132
Um, unaweza kunipa nafasi
ya kuifikiria, tafadhali?

1071
01:13:07,166 --> 01:13:08,766
<i>Bila shaka. Nilitaka tu</i>

1072
01:13:08,800 --> 01:13:10,132
kushiriki habari njema.

1073
01:13:10,166 --> 01:13:12,033
Heri ya Mwaka Mpya, Tess.

1074
01:13:12,065 --> 01:13:14,166
Heri ya Mwaka Mpya, bwana.

1075
01:13:16,966 --> 01:13:18,300
Habari.

1076
01:13:18,332 --> 01:13:20,332
Ulikuwa ukizungumza nami?

1077
01:13:20,365 --> 01:13:21,833
Hapana.

1078
01:13:21,867 --> 01:13:24,100
Kwa nini inachukua muda mrefu hivi?

1079
01:13:24,132 --> 01:13:25,833
Kuwa mwanamke.

1080
01:13:25,867 --> 01:13:28,100
Sasa, unaweza kwenda kusubiri nje?

1081
01:13:28,132 --> 01:13:30,233
- Pole sana.
- Asante.

1082
01:13:40,065 --> 01:13:42,166
Bila kushindwa!

1083
01:13:43,000 --> 01:13:44,365
Pumbavu!

1084
01:13:44,399 --> 01:13:47,100
- Ni sawa.
- Pole. Pole.

1085
01:13:49,899 --> 01:13:51,399
Tumekukumbuka.

1086
01:13:51,432 --> 01:13:52,698
Tuko sawa?

1087
01:13:52,733 --> 01:13:54,399
Historia ya kale.

1088
01:13:54,432 --> 01:13:55,966
Mnataka
kujiunga na hili?

1089
01:13:55,998 --> 01:13:57,233
Ndiyo, unaweza
kuchukua nafasi yangu.

1090
01:13:57,265 --> 01:13:59,365
Nenda. Nitatazama.

1091
01:14:00,332 --> 01:14:01,934
Napenda kutazama.

1092
01:14:01,966 --> 01:14:04,132
Ndiyo, nina hakika unapenda.

1093
01:14:04,166 --> 01:14:06,233
