Alaa... lakini ndivyo ilivyo.

1177
01:18:26,932 --> 01:18:28,966
Wewe unaamini kila kitu
kinachotoka kinywani mwake.

1178
01:18:28,998 --> 01:18:30,765
Ninakuchukia sana, Molly.

1179
01:18:30,798 --> 01:18:32,199
