imenifikisha wapi?

1255
01:23:16,731 --> 01:23:19,765
Hutanisamehe kamwe,
sivyo?

1256
01:23:19,798 --> 01:23:22,167
Utaendelea tu kuikumbushia
kila wakati.

1257
01:23:22,201 --> 01:23:24,798
Kwa sababu sikuamini!

1258
01:23:25,100 --> 01:23:28,367
Unajifanya kana kwamba
wewe huna hatia hata kidogo.

1259
01:23:28,400 --> 01:23:30,201
