1263
01:23:35,134 --> 01:23:36,998
Potea hapa!

1264
01:23:45,367 --> 01:23:47,666
Hardin.

1265
01:23:49,865 --> 01:23:51,966
Hardin?

1266
01:24:16,666 --> 01:24:18,266
Hujambo.

1267
01:24:18,301 --> 01:24:19,932
Hujambo.

