na isiyo na furaha.</i>

1318
01:28:08,233 --> 01:28:10,798
<i>"Nilifikiri tulikuwa na nafasi
ya kupata furaha,</i>

1319
01:28:10,832 --> 01:28:12,966
<i>"lakini mwishowe,
haikukusudiwa kuwa.</i>

1320
01:28:13,000 --> 01:28:15,698
<i>"Nakupenda
kwa moyo wangu wote,</i>

1321
01:28:15,731 --> 01:28:18,832
<i>"na hiyo ndiyo sababu hasa niliyohitaji kwenda
mbali nawe iwezekanavyo.</i>

1322
01:28:18,867 --> 01:28:22,033
<i>"Sisi ni kama uraibu kwa kila
mmoja, tukiwa na sehemu sawa za raha...</i>

1323
01:28:22,067 --> 01:28:23,966
- <i>"na maumivu."</i>
- Kwa sababu sikuamini!

1324
01:28:24,000 --> 01:28:25,833
<i>"Na kuhusu ule usiku mwingine,
yule msichana,</i>

1325
01:28:25,867 --> 01:28:28,233
<i>"alikuwa mmoja wa
wanawake niliowahi kuwa nao zamani.</i>

1326
01:28:28,265 --> 01:28:32,233
<i>"Ilinibidi niombe radhi kwa maisha yangu ya nyuma
ili niwe na maisha ya baadaye nawe,</i>

1327
01:28:32,265 --> 01:28:36,332
<i>"lakini majaliwa tu...
yanaonekana kutuzuia.</i>

1328
01:28:38,067 --> 01:28:40,067
<i>"Basi tuache upuuzi.</i>

1329
01:28:40,100 --> 01:28:42,698
<i>"Wewe ni mzuri kupita kiasi kwangu,
na ninajua hilo.</i>

1330
01:28:42,731 --> 01:28:44,100
<i>"Na mahali fulani
ndani ya akili yangu</i>

1331
01:28:44,132 --> 01:28:46,631
<i>"daima nilijua
tusingedumu,</i>

1332
01:28:46,666 --> 01:28:48,300
<i>"na nadhani hata wewe ulijua.</i>

1333
01:28:48,332 --> 01:28:50,731
<i>"Najua hili litakuwa
na maumivu mwanzoni,</i>

1334
01:28:50,765 --> 01:28:53,033
<i>"na linaweza kuchukua siku kadhaa,
au hata zaidi.</i>

1335
01:28:53,067 --> 01:28:56,033
<i>"Lakini moja ya siku hizo,
utakuja kuamka</i>

1336
01:28:56,067 --> 01:28:59,233
<i>"na huzuni itaanza
kutoweka...</i>

1337
01:28:59,265 --> 01:29:03,631
<i>"hadi tuwe kitu kingine
ila kumbukumbu ya mbali.</i>

1338
01:29:03,666 --> 01:29:05,765
<i>Kwaheri, Tessa."</i>

1339
01:29:25,166 --> 01:29:28,399
Lazima unipigie simu.

1340
01:29:28,432 --> 01:29:31,666
Tunahitaji kuzungumza kuhusu hili,
sawa?

1341
01:29:31,698 --> 01:29:34,631
Huwezi kutoweka kwa siku tisa. Nipigie simu.

1342
01:29:34,666 --> 01:29:36,800
Nipigie simu.

1343
01:29:46,265 --> 01:29:48,132
Tessa?!

1344
01:29:48,166 --> 01:29:49,365
Hardin, nisaidie!

1345
01:29:55,833 --> 01:29:58,166
Ni sawa.

1346
01:30:32,833 --> 01:30:34,966
Asante.

1347
01:30:34,998 --> 01:30:38,132
Maombi
yanaendeleaje?

1348
01:30:38,166 --> 01:30:41,300
Vyema. Baba alisema
angepiga simu kadhaa.

1349
01:30:42,833 --> 01:30:45,033
Ninyi wawili mlizungumza?

1350
01:30:45,065 --> 01:30:47,166
Iliendaje?

1351
01:30:48,733 --> 01:30:50,833
Vile ambavyo ingewezekana.

1352
01:30:52,132 --> 01:30:54,365
Hardin, kilichotokea
usiku ule,

1353
01:30:54,399 --> 01:30:56,065
haikuwa kosa lake.

1354
01:30:56,100 --> 01:30:58,332
Na usiku mwingine wote?

1355
01:30:58,365 --> 01:31:00,666
Si kosa lake?

1356
01:31:02,199 --> 01:31:04,300
Ndiyo, mambo yalikuwa hovyo.

1357
01:31:04,599 --> 01:31:07,699
Mambo yalikuwa hovyo, na sote
tulistahili bora zaidi.

1358
01:31:07,733 --> 01:31:09,265
Lakini mtu pekee
unayemuadhibu

1359
01:31:09,300 --> 01:31:11,033
kwa kutomsamehe
ni wewe mwenyewe.

1360
01:31:11,065 --> 01:31:15,766
Na Hardin, nataka
uache kujiadhibu mwenyewe.

1361
01:31:16,631 --> 01:31:18,800
Kwa hivyo unafikiri ni haki kwamba anapata kuishi katika

1362
01:31:18,833 --> 01:31:22,399
nyumba hiyo kubwa na ya kifahari, na wewe uko hapa peke yako?

1363
01:31:22,432 --> 01:31:24,699
Nani amesema niko peke yangu?

1364
01:31:24,733 --> 01:31:27,065
Nini?
Unatoka na mtu?

1365
01:31:27,100 --> 01:31:31,199
- Huna haja ya kuonekana umeshangaa hivyo.
- Nani?

1366
01:31:31,533 --> 01:31:33,833
- Mike.
- Mike?

1367
01:31:34,132 --> 01:31:36,899
- Mike yule bwege wa mlango wa jirani?
- Yeye <i>si</i> bwege!

1368
01:31:36,934 --> 01:31:39,667
- Yeye ni bwege kiasi.
- Ni mwanamume mwema sana,

1369
01:31:39,699 --> 01:31:41,667
na ananitendea vizuri.

1370
01:31:41,699 --> 01:31:43,998
Ndiyo, ni heri afanye hivyo.

1371
01:31:44,766 --> 01:31:48,199
Ulisikia kwamba Vance alikuwa anahamia Seattle?

1372
01:31:48,233 --> 01:31:50,766
Tessa anaenda pia.
Ulijuaje?

1373
01:31:50,800 --> 01:31:52,800
Naam, tunazungumza
mara kwa mara.

1374
01:31:52,833 --> 01:31:55,065
Anaandaa sherehe ya kuagana
Jumapili,

1375
01:31:55,100 --> 01:31:58,733
na nafikiri unapaswa kuondoka
kwenye sofa hii na kwenda kumchukua.

1376
01:31:58,766 --> 01:32:03,033
- Hapana, siwezi.
- Huwezi? Au hutaki kukabiliana na ulichokiacha nyuma?

1377
01:32:03,065 --> 01:32:04,332
Itanibidi niondoke sasa hivi.

1378
01:32:04,365 --> 01:32:06,766
Sasa unasubiri nini?

1379
01:32:06,800 --> 01:32:09,365
- Mama, sita...
- Hardin...

1380
01:32:09,399 --> 01:32:15,733
Nakupenda, lakini <i>lazima</i> uanze
kupigania kile ambacho ni muhimu kweli.

1381
01:32:25,667 --> 01:32:27,365
<i>Asanteni sana nyote
kwa kuja.</i>

1382
01:32:27,399 --> 01:32:31,632
Inamaanisha kila kitu kwangu kuwa na
kila mtu ninayempenda hapa nasi.

1383
01:32:31,667 --> 01:32:33,766
Nina... fahari kupita kiasi

1384
01:32:34,065 --> 01:32:35,998
kwa kazi ambayo kila mtu
katika chumba hiki amefanya,

1385
01:32:36,033 --> 01:32:37,998
lakini kuna mtu mmoja
mahususi

1386
01:32:38,033 --> 01:32:40,233
ambaye nisingeweza kufanya
haya yote bila yeye.

1387
01:32:40,265 --> 01:32:41,699
Na huyo ni Kimberly.

1388
01:32:47,332 --> 01:32:49,300
Mimi na Smith tulikuwa tunazungumza
siku nyingine,

1389
01:32:49,332 --> 01:32:51,332
na akasema, "Baba,
sherehe za kuagana zina huzuni kiasi."

1390
01:32:51,365 --> 01:32:53,300
Na ana hoja.

1391
01:32:53,332 --> 01:32:55,899
Na tukawa tunawaza,
"Tunawezaje kufanya hii iwe sherehe?"

1392
01:32:55,932 --> 01:32:57,998
Kisha tukapata wazo.

1393
01:33:02,865 --> 01:33:05,998
Kimberly...

1394
01:33:06,899 --> 01:33:09,966
utafunga ndoa na baba yangu
na kuwa mama yangu wa kambo?

1395
01:33:09,998 --> 01:33:12,100
Aww...

1396
01:33:13,100 --> 01:33:15,300
Ndiyo!

1397
01:33:15,332 --> 01:33:17,199
Ndiyo!

1398
01:33:21,233 --> 01:33:22,832
Vipi kuhusu mimi?

1399
01:33:25,100 --> 01:33:27,733
- Aww...
- Safi sana!

1400
01:33:38,966 --> 01:33:40,733
Nani amesema miisho ya furaha
haipo?

1401
01:33:40,766 --> 01:33:42,332
Usiniambie.
Wewe ni mtu mwenye shaka.

1402
01:33:42,365 --> 01:33:45,233
Ninaanza ukurasa
mpya.

1403
01:33:45,265 --> 01:33:48,199
Unapendeza sana,
hata hivyo.

1404
01:33:48,233 --> 01:33:52,733
Kwa hiyo... umeshaamua
kuhusu Seattle?

1405
01:33:52,966 --> 01:33:55,365
Naam, sioni
sababu kubwa

1406
01:33:55,399 --> 01:33:58,899
ya kuacha fursa hiyo
tena.

1407
01:34:00,233 --> 01:34:01,699
Hiyo ni...

1408
01:34:01,733 --> 01:34:02,733
nzuri sana kusikia.

1409
01:34:04,399 --> 01:34:06,233
Tazama, Tessa,
kuna jambo

1410
01:34:06,265 --> 01:34:08,265
ambalo kwa kweli nataka
kulitua kifuani mwangu.

1411
01:34:08,300 --> 01:34:10,600
Sawa.

1412
01:34:10,865 --> 01:34:14,233
Uh, siku ile,
hospitalini...

1413
01:34:14,265 --> 01:34:16,132
Nilipokea simu yako ya mkononi,

1414
01:34:16,166 --> 01:34:17,966
alikuwa Hardin,

1415
01:34:17,998 --> 01:34:21,199
na nikamwambia
akae mbali nawe.

1416
01:34:21,233 --> 01:34:23,100
- Nini?
- Nikitafakari,

1417
01:34:23,132 --> 01:34:25,765
natambua kwamba
hilo lilivuka mpaka,

1418
01:34:25,798 --> 01:34:29,733
na natambua kwamba niliruhusu
hisia zangu zinitawale,

1419
01:34:29,765 --> 01:34:31,865
na samahani,

1420
01:34:31,899 --> 01:34:36,033
lakini kwa namna fulani unatoa
upande huo ndani yangu, kwa hiyo...

1421
01:34:37,300 --> 01:34:39,600
Sawa.

1422
01:34:41,233 --> 01:34:43,033
Uko sawa?

1423
01:34:43,065 --> 01:34:44,932
Eh.

1424
01:34:44,966 --> 01:34:47,132
Kwa kweli kuna
mengi zaidi ningependa kusema,

1425
01:34:47,166 --> 01:34:48,932
- lakini naomba unisamehe kwa muda kidogo?
- Ndiyo.

1426
01:34:48,966 --> 01:34:51,065
Asante.

1427
01:35:13,033 --> 01:35:15,132
Samahani sana.

1428
01:35:26,798 --> 01:35:28,899
Lahaula.

1429
01:35:32,731 --> 01:35:34,065
Aliondoka kupitia mbele.

1430
01:35:34,100 --> 01:35:36,199
Asante.

1431
01:35:40,698 --> 01:35:42,798
Tessa!

1432
01:35:56,365 --> 01:36:00,966
Hautaniacha kamwe,
sivyo?

1433
01:36:23,966 --> 01:36:26,065
Nilijaribu.

1434
01:37:23,966 --> 01:37:26,199
Kwa hiyo, ninyi wawili mlikuwa
na Krismasi njema?

1435
01:37:26,233 --> 01:37:28,301
Sa-wa,
huzungumzi.

1436
01:37:28,333 --> 01:37:31,065
Basi... haya, basi <i>mimi</i> nilikuwa naota
Krismasi ya theluji.

1437
01:37:31,100 --> 01:37:32,966
Hmph! Nilichopata ni joto tu.

1438
01:37:32,998 --> 01:37:35,400
Unajua, nachukia joto.

1439
01:37:35,434 --> 01:37:37,832
Joto huingia akilini mwa watu

1440
01:37:37,865 --> 01:37:40,798
na kuwafanya wafanye
mambo ya kichaa.

1441
01:37:54,865 --> 01:37:56,932
<i>Kama nilivyosema,</i>

1442
01:37:56,966 --> 01:38:00,266
<i>hii ni hadithi
uliyowahi kuisikia hapo awali.</i>

1443
01:38:00,301 --> 01:38:03,731
<i>Tofauti pekee ni,
hii ni hadithi </i>yetu.<i></i>

1444
01:38:03,765 --> 01:38:05,865
<i>Ya Tessa na yangu.</i>

1445
01:38:06,467 --> 01:38:08,666
"Sitaki kamwe
kutengwa nawe

1446
01:38:08,698 --> 01:38:10,798
tangu leo na kuendelea."

1447
01:38:15,100 --> 01:38:16,932
<i>Na nani anayejua?</i>

1448
01:38:16,966 --> 01:38:20,698
<i>Labda kuna mwisho mwema
kwa ajili yetu baada ya yote.</i>

1449
01:38:20,731 --> 01:38:22,132
Tess.

1450
01:38:22,166 --> 01:38:24,666
- Habari...
- Hardin!

1451
01:38:26,033 --> 01:38:28,132
- Baba?
- "Baba"?

1452
01:38:28,998 --> 01:38:31,166
<i>Nadhani itabidi
tugundue tu.</i>

1453
01:40:09,500 --> 01:40:11,932
Tessa.
Tessa.

1454
01:40:11,966 --> 01:40:13,100
Tessa.

1455
01:40:13,134 --> 01:40:14,899
Je, unapenda kwenda matembezini?

1456
01:40:14,932 --> 01:40:16,234
Kwa sababu mimi sipendi.

1457
01:40:16,266 --> 01:40:18,765
Lakini m-mimi nitaenda... nawe.

1458
01:40:19,698 --> 01:40:21,201
Kama unataka kwenda.

1459
01:40:22,899 --> 01:40:23,899
Tessa.

1460
01:40:23,932 --> 01:40:25,899
Hiyo inatisha sana.

1461
01:40:25,932 --> 01:40:27,899
Nimekuwa nikitaka kukuambia
jambo fulani kwa muda mrefu,

1462
01:40:27,932 --> 01:40:30,167
na sababu
ambayo sijakuambia

1463
01:40:30,201 --> 01:40:32,631
ni kwa sababu ya Idara ya Rasilimali Watu
kazini.

1464
01:40:32,666 --> 01:40:34,201
Usizungumze kuhusu
Idara ya Rasilimali Watu.

1465
01:40:34,234 --> 01:40:35,998
Hiyo si... ya kuvutia.

1466
01:40:36,033 --> 01:40:37,367
Tessa!

1467
01:40:37,399 --> 01:40:39,100
Usitumie kidole.

1468
01:40:39,134 --> 01:40:40,266
Kiweke <i>chini!</i>

1469
01:40:40,301 --> 01:40:42,631
Mimi huvaa tu suti yangu ya kijani-samawati

1470
01:40:42,666 --> 01:40:44,731
wakati nina jambo
muhimu la kusema.

1471
01:40:44,765 --> 01:40:46,399
Kuna mtu.

1472
01:40:46,432 --> 01:40:48,631
Tessa.

1473
01:40:48,666 --> 01:40:50,333
Kuna bafu nyingine
ndani ya nyumba

1474
01:40:50,367 --> 01:40:53,065
ikiwa unahitaji kwenda kiasi hicho.

1475
01:40:54,367 --> 01:40:56,832
Nenda tu.

1476
01:40:56,865 --> 01:40:58,966
Ndiyo. Unaweza kwenda sasa.

1477
01:41:03,251 --> 01:41:08,251
Manukuu na explosiveskull
